Cp%3EMakhachkala%2C%20a%20city%20of%20over%20600%2C000%20on%20the%20Caspian%20Sea%2C%20is%20the%20capital%20of%20Dagestan%2C%20a%20Russian%20republic%20bordering%20Chechnya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blast%20was%20heard%20shortly%20before%2010%3A00%20pm%20(1900%20GMT)%20on%20Monday%2C%20Sergei%20Melikov%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Dagestan%20administration%2C%20announced%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20witness%20quoted%20by%20Russian%20daily%20newspaper%20Izvestia%20said%20the%20fire%20started%20in%20an%20area%20where%20cars%20were%20parked%20and%20spread%20to%20the%20petrol%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20explosion%2C%20everything%20fell%20on%20our%20heads.%20We%20couldn't%20see%20anything%20any%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20witness%2C%20who%20was%20not%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideo%20footage%20released%20by%20Russia's%20emergency%20situations%20ministry%20showed%20firefighters%20trying%20to%20extinguish%20huge%20flames%20near%20burnt-out%20vehicles%2C%20as%20rescue%20workers%20examined%20the%20rubble%20of%20a%20building%20with%20flashlights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20had%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20around%20600%20square%20metres%20(6%2C450%20square%20feet)%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20260%20firefighters%20had%20been%20deployed%20ot%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20Il-76%20aircraft%20carrying%20medical%20equipment%20had%20been%20dispatched%20to%20Makhachkala%20to%20evacuate%20the%20seriously%20injured%20to%20Moscow%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelikov%20said%20that%20the%20evacuation%20operation%20had%20since%20been%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dagestan%20government%20declared%20August%2015%20a%20day%20of%20mourning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BState%20flags%20will%20be%20flown%20at%20half%20mast%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20and%20cultural%20institutions%20and%20TV%20channels%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20cancel%20entertainment%20events%20and%20progr