22title%22%3A%22Will%20the%20G20%20Stand%20Against%20the%20'Bulldozer%20Tactics'%20Deployed%20by%20the%20US%20to%20Weaken%20WTO%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West%2C%20led%20mainly%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20over%20the%20multilateral%20trade%20structures%20built%20by%20it%20painstakingly%20over%20the%20past%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20a%20variety%20of%20the%20bulldozer%20virus%20seems%20to%20be%20striking%20at%20the%20roots%20of%20multilateral%20trade%20agreements%20that%20governed%20global%20trade%20since%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnsurprisingly%2C%20the%20developing%20and%20the%20poorest%20countries%20are%20left%20to%20face%20new%20forms%20of%20the%20law%20of%20the%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20is%20no%20clear%20definition%20of%20what%20would%20constitute%20the%20bulldozer%20virus%2C%20it%2C%20however%2C%20broadly%20indicates%20an%20unprecedented%20assault%20on%20democratic%20institutions%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20whether%20in%20the%20domestic%20context%20or%20in%20the%20international%2C%20rule-based%2C%20member-driven%2C%20intergovernmental%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20covered%20the%20global%20trading%20system%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%2C%20which%20is%20reckoned%20as%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20rule-based%20multilateral%20trading%20system%2C%20since%201990%2C%20the%20focus%20here%20is%20on%20the%20chilling%20effect%20of%20the%20bulldozer%20trade%20measure%20being%20deployed%20almost%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20August%209%2C%20the%20US%20%E2%80%9Cprohibited%20Americans%20from%20investing%20in%20some%20Chinese%20companies%20developing%20advanced%20semiconductors%20and%20quantum%20computers%20starting%20next%20year%2C%20escalating%20Washington%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20Beijing%20from%20producing%20cutting-edge%20technology%20for%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fu-s-to-ban-some-investments-in-china-71f519d6%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%3Emilitary%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20move%20could%20unsettle%20fragile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fjanet-yellen-says-u-s-china-making-progress-on-managing-economic-tensions-1e2c07%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%3Eefforts%20to%20rekindle%20diplomatic%20relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20%3Cem%3EWSJ%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20suggested%20that%20%E2%80%9Cbeyond%20banning%20new%20private-equity%2C%20venture-capital%20and%20joint-venture%20investments%20in%20advanced%20semiconductors%20and%20quantum%20computers%2C%20the%20executive%20order%20will%20also%20require%20Americans%20doing%20business%20in%20China%20to%20inform%20the%20US%20government%20about%20direct%20investments%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20other%20types%20of%20semiconductors%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPink%20City%20meeting%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20G20%20trade%20ministerial%20meeting%20of%20industrialised%20and%20developing%20countries%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20seven-star%20hotel%2C%20Rambagh%20Palace%2C%20in%20the%20Pink%20City%20of%20Jaipur%20assumes%20importance.%20The%20central%20issue%20is%20how%20to%20stop%20the%20bulldozer%20trade%20measures%20and%20policies%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%20United%20States%20as%20well%20as%20the%20European%20Union%20in%20the%20recent%20flurry%20of%20unilateral%20trade-related%20environment%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20seems%20determined%20to%20decimate%20the%20two-tier%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%20The%20WTO%20was%20established%20after%20the%20Uruguay%20Round%20of%20trade%20negotiations%20in%201995%20to%20replace%20the%20General%20Agreement%20on%20Tariffs%20and%20Trade%20that%20was%20established%20after%20the%20Geneva%20Round%20of%20trade%20negotiations%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15141824%2FGeneva_Ministerial_Conference_18-20_May_1998_9305956531.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15141824%2FGeneva_Ministerial_Conference_18-20_May_1998_9305956531.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15141824%2FGeneva_Ministerial_Conference_18-20_May_1998_9305956531-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15141824%2FGeneva_Ministerial_Conference_18-20_May_1998_9305956531-1024x681.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668194%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Geneva%20Ministerial%20Conference%20in%20May%201998.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FWorld%20Trade%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20the%20US%20and%20EU%20appear%20ready%20to%20dismantle%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Change%20Agreement%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fprocess-and-meetings%2Fthe-paris-agreement%5C%22%3EThe%20Paris%20Agreement%20%7C%20UNFCCC%3C%2Fa%3E).%20The%20rapid%20spread%20of%20bulldozer%20trade-related%20environment%20measures%20is%20gaining%20currency%20both%20in%20the%20national%20and%20multilateral%20organisations.%20It%20seems%20to%20vindicate%20the%20repeat%20of%20those%20horrifying%20developments%20that%20followed%20after%20the%20first%20World%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20India%20would%20resolve%20the%20issue%20of%20bulldozer%20measures%20for%20atrophying%20the%20two-stage%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20that%20has%20been%20the%20hallmark%20of%20resolving%20global%20trade%20disputes%20since%201995%20or%20making%20the%20Paris%20climate%20change%20agreement%20redundant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20meeting%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20India%2C%20on%20August%2025-26%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20focus%20a%20great%20deal%20on%20reforming%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%20The%20discussions%20and%20the%20final%20text%20negotiated%20by%20G20%20Sherpas%2C%20which%20will%20be%20further%20finetuned%20with%20last-minute%20additions%2C%20could%20test%20the%20resolve%20of%20New%20Delhi%20in%20accommodating%20the%20bulldozer%20measures%20being%20deployed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20the%20EU%20in%20the%20multilateral%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20trade%20or%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-day%20ministerial%20meeting%20in%20Jaipur%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20preceded%20by%20senior%20officials%20meeting%20for%20three%20days%20starting%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20G20%20officials%2Fsherpas%20from%2019%20countries%20are%20expected%20to%20negotiate%20texts%20in%20which%20India%2C%20as%20the%20chair%20and%20host%20of%20the%20conference%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20every%20effort%20possible%20to%20bring%20about%20convergence%20in%20apparently%20five%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20include%20logistics%2C%20global%20value%20chains%2C%20WTO%20reforms%2C%20MSMEs%20(micro%2C%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises)%20and%20their%20importance%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20and%20perhaps%2C%20issues%20concerning%20food%20security%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20comprises%20Argentina%2C%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Canada%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20India%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Russia%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Turkey%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20plus%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20texts%20likely%20to%20emerge%20after%20the%20negotiations%20may%20seem%20like%20balanced%20agreements%20of%20convergence%20in%20these%20five%20areas%2C%20but%20they%20may%20not%20substantively%20address%20the%20real%20issues%20in%20the%20WTO%20reform%2C%20especially%20the%20dispute%20settlement%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20G20%20texts%20matter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20since%20its%20inception%20in%20the%20shadows%20of%20the%20worst%20financial%20crisis%20of%202008%2C%20the%20value%20of%20the%20outcomes%20in%20successive%20meetings%20appears%20exceptionally%20limited%2C%20because%20they%20are%20neither%20binding%20on%20the%20G20%20members%20nor%20they%20could%20influence%20developments%20at%20other%20multilateral%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Bali%20G20%20declaration%20was%20issued%20last%20year%20when%20the%20Presidents%20of%20the%20US%20and%20China%20agreed%20to%20work%20together%20and%20cooperatively%20to%20resolve%20the%20multilateral%20issues%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20went%20their%20ways%20intensifying%20the%20cold%20war%20on%20semiconductors%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20investment%20and%20finance-related%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20limited%20value%20is%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20G20%20sherpas%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20final%20texts%20that%20they%20had%20negotiated.%20Having%20covered%20two%20G20%20meetings%20in%20Turkey%20and%20Hamburg%20(Germany)%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20texts%20tend%20to%20vastly%20dilute%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20any%20outcomes%20reached%20at%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FOpinion%2FHOfUiWqardeXKQsS12PFXM%2FG20-leaders-fail-to-generate-international-economic-cooper.html%5C%22%3Emeetings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20purpose%20of%20the%20G20%20meetings%20is%20that%20they%20provide%20space%20for%20bilateral%20meetings%20among%20the%2019%20countries%20in%20different%20configurations%20during%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20purpose%20%E2%80%93%20as%20witnessed%20by%20this%20writer%20in%20Turkey%20and%20Germany%20%E2%80%93%20is%20for%20the%20host%2C%20either%20the%20president%20or%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20to%20receive%20his%20counterparts%20for%20a%20photo%20opportunity%20and%20escort%20them%20into%20the%20main%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20bound%20to%20maximise%20the%20value.%20Maybe%20it%20will%20become%20handy%20for%20his%20propaganda%20efforts%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%20ministerial%20summit%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20G20%20trade%20ministerial%20meeting%2C%20it%20is%20well%20known%20that%20the%20continued%20divergences%20between%20the%20US%20and%20one%20or%20two%20members%20on%20the%20one%20side%2C%20and%20developing%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Brazil%2C%20on%20the%20other%2C%20seem%20somewhat%20irreconcilable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20may%20try%20hard%20to%20press%20for%20some%20real%2Ffundamental%20outcomes%20in%20ensuring%20a%20robust%20dispute%20settlement%20system%2C%20but%20the%20chances%20seem%20somewhat%20bleak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20somewhat%20difficult%20for%20India%20and%20other%20few%20developing%20country%20allies%20to%20insert%20any%20strong%20language%20on%20preserving%2Fsafeguarding%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%20two-tier%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20(DSS)%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20alleged%20bulldozer%20onslaught%20to%20kill%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20as%20suggested%20by%20the%20former%20US%20trade%20representative%20Ambassador%20Robert%20Lighthizer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20the%20EU%20and%20US%20are%20embarking%20on%20unilateral%20carbon%20border%20tax%20measures%20in%20apparent%20violation%20of%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20and%20WTO%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20emerging%20comradery%2C%20the%20US%20may%20not%20choose%20to%20embarrass%20India%20at%20the%20meeting%20and%20unlikely%20to%20dent%20India%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20on%20dispute%20settlement%20(DS)%20reform%20by%20agreeing%20to%20a%20two-stage%20dispute%20settlement%20system%2C%20and%20even%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20(AB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20may%20not%20mean%20much%20since%20Washington%20wants%20to%20bring%20the%20DSS%20(dispute%20settlement%20system)%20that%20undergirds%20the%20enforcement%20function%20of%20the%20WTO%20since%201995%2C%20as%20it%20seems%20bent%20on%20permanently%20paralyzing%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20to%20an%20extent%20that%20its%20presence%20could%20seem%20like%20the%20proverbial%20patient%20caught%20up%20in%20a%20chronic%20illness%20and%20starvation%20(like%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20latest%20bulldozer%20developments%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnuh-demolitions-residents-due-process-damages%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E)%20unable%20to%20perform%20any%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20binding%20rulings%20of%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20since%201995%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20WTO%20was%20established%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20its%20raison%20d%E2%80%99etre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EWTO%20dispute%20settlement%20reform%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20dispute%20settlement%20reform%20is%20mandated%20by%20trade%20ministers%20at%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%2012th%20ministerial%20conference%20(MC12)%20last%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParagraph%20four%20of%20the%20Outcome%20Document%20of%20MC12%20states%20somewhat%20ambiguously%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20acknowledge%20the%20challenges%20and%20concerns%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20dispute%20settlement%20system%2C%20including%20those%20related%20to%20the%20Appellate%20Body%2C%20recognize%20the%20importance%20and%20urgency%20of%20addressing%20those%20challenges%20and%20concerns%2C%20and%20commit%20to%20conduct%20discussions%20with%20the%20view%20to%20having%20a%20fully%20and%20well-functioning%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20accessible%20to%20all%20Members%20by%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Geneva%20mandate%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20explicitly%20mention%20restoring%20the%20two-stage%20DSS%20as%20it%20existed%20till%20December%202019%2C%20a%20large%20majority%20of%20members%20have%20continually%20underscored%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20two-stage%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20with%20an%20un-weakened%20Appellate%20Body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15142339%2FEntr%25C3%25A9e_de_lOMC_%25C3%25A0_Gen%25C3%25A8ve.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15142339%2FEntr%25C3%25A9e_de_lOMC_%25C3%25A0_Gen%25C3%25A8ve.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15142339%2FEntr%25C3%25A9e_de_lOMC_%25C3%25A0_Gen%25C3%25A8ve-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15142339%2FEntr%25C3%25A9e_de_lOMC_%25C3%25A0_Gen%25C3%25A8ve-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668197%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWorld%20Trade%20Organization%20headquarters%20in%20Geneva.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FCC0%201.0G%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20may%20say%20that%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20two-tier%20DSS%20but%20with%20an%20Appellate%C2%A0Body%20that%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20teeth%E2%80%9D%20to%20rectify%20the%20egregious%20trade%20measures%20adopted%20by%20any%20member%2C%20particularly%20itself%2C%20said%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20remains%20firm%20in%20its%20stance%20on%20allegedly%20converting%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20into%20a%20proverbial%20%E2%80%9Cvegetable%E2%80%9D%2C%20going%20by%20the%20continuity%20of%20the%20stand%20taken%20between%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20the%20Biden%20administration%20with%20inconsequential%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20(USTR)%20Ambassador%20Robert%20Lighthizer%20praised%20his%20successor%20Ambassador%20Katherine%20Tai%20when%20she%20said%20that%20the%20WTO%20is%20on%20very%2C%20very%20thin%20ice%20and%20it%20really%20challenges%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20system%20when%20two%20panels%20struck%20down%20measures%20imposed%20on%20grounds%20of%20national%20security%20considerations.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Killing%20the%20appellate%20body%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Appellate%20Body%2C%20which%20has%20passed%20rulings%20in%20hundreds%20of%20trade%20disputes%20among%20WTO%20members%2C%20is%20described%20as%20the%20Jewel%20of%20the%20Crown.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20made%20dysfunctional%20since%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Uncle%20Sam%20blocked%20the%20filling%20of%20seven%20vacancies.%20Despite%2C%20repeated%20demands%20by%20around%20130%20members%20to%20fill%20the%20vacancies%20expeditiously%2C%20the%20US%20showed%20no%20remorse%20in%20the%20last%2067%20sittings%20of%20the%20dispute%20settlement%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20%E2%80%9Ckilling%20the%20Appellate%20Body%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20as%20proposed%20by%20Ambassador%20Lighthizer%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Biden%20administration%20may%20follow%20the%20popular%20song%20%E2%80%9CKilling%20me%20softly%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20latest%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3ENo%20Trade%20is%20Free%3A%20Changing%20Course%2C%20Taking%20on%20China%2C%20and%20Helping%20America%E2%80%99s%20Workers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20former%20USTR%20Ambassador%20Lighthizer%2C%20a%20key%20official%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20seems%20to%20play%20the%20victim%20card%20like%20his%20former%20boss%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20facing%20several%20legal%20challenges%2C%20said%20an%20official%20who%20read%20Ambassador%20Lighthizer%E2%80%99s%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20majoritarian%20politics%2C%20which%20is%20in%20full%20display%20in%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20in%20the%20host%20country%20of%20the%20G20%20meeting%2C%20the%20US%20is%20playing%20a%20similar%20victim%20card%20to%20claim%20that%20it%20has%20been%20given%20a%20raw%20deal%20at%20the%20WTO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbassador%20Lighthizer%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20must%20be%20done%20to%20fix%20the%20WTO%E2%80%9D%2C%20emphasising%20that%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20is%20arguing%20that%20we%20should%20revert%20from%20a%20rules-based%20system%20to%20the%20so-called%20law%20of%20the%20jungle%20in%20trade%20relations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20sticking%20with%20the%20current%20WTO%20would%20actually%20entail%20betraying%20the%20core%20principles%20of%20a%20rules-based%20system%2C%20because%20this%20organisation%20has%20shown%20itself%20to%20be%20chronically%20incapable%20of%20proceeding%20according%20to%20those%20principles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%2C%20with%20some%20alleged%20degree%20of%20sophistry%2C%20is%20essentially%20following%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20said%20negotiators%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20DS%20reform%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20US%20is%20now%20pursuing%20unilateral%20measures%20like%20the%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20subsidies%20being%20provided%20to%20promote%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%E2%80%9D%20industrialisation%20as%20well%20as%20for%20transforming%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20in%20ways%20that%20China%20can%20never%20compete%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbassador%20Lighthizer%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20should%20be%20scrapped%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20new%20one%2C%20modeled%20after%20commercial%20arbitration%2C%20should%20be%20put%20in%20its%20place.%20There%20should%20be%20a%20one-stage%20panel%20process%20with%20a%20vote%20of%20the%20WTO%20member%20states%20being%20able%20to%20overturn%20the%20decisions.%20Further%2C%20the%20decisions%20should%20be%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20party%20negotiations%20and%20not%20be%20binding.%20The%20strawman%20of%20the%20law%20of%20the%20jungle%20versus%20the%20status%20quo%20cannot%20obscure%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20current%20system%20is%20a%20massive%20failure%20on%20its%20own%20terms%20%E2%80%93%20and%20certainly%20with%20respect%20to%20US%20interests.%20The%20status%20quo%20is%20not%20an%20option.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20DS%20discussions%2C%20the%20US%20seems%20to%20be%20adopting%20the%20diktats%20pronounced%20by%20Ambassador%20Lighthizer.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20US%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20spelling%20out%20its%20views%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20the%20face%20of%20growing%20opposition%20to%20some%20of%20its%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20the%20US%20proposal%20on%20Appellate%20Review%20in%20the%20ongoing%20DS%20discussions%20was%20rebuffed%20in%20what%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20its%20move%20to%20practically%20eliminate%20the%20Appellate%20Body%2C%20said%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20informal%20discussions%20chaired%20by%20the%20facilitator%2C%20Marco%20Molina%2C%20deputy%20trade%20envoy%20of%20Guatemala%2C%20on%20June%208%2C%20several%20countries%20including%20China%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20South%20Africa%20appear%20to%20have%20opposed%20the%20US%20proposal%2C%20said%20participants%20familiar%20with%20the%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20plenary%20meeting%2C%20the%20facilitator%20tried%20hard%20the%20whole%20day%20(two%20sessions%20of%20three%20hours%20each)%20to%20see%20if%20the%20members%20could%20make%20progress%20on%20the%20US%20proposal%2C%20but%20his%20attempts%20were%20proved%20to%20be%20in%20vain%2C%20said%20people%2C%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20proposal%20on%20Appellate%20Review%20in%20the%20facilitator%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20Yellow%20Box%20of%20proposals%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20more%20refined%20for%20further%20discussions%2C%20calls%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Camendment%E2%80%9D%20to%20Article%2017.2%20of%20the%20Dispute%20Settlement%20Understanding%20to%20expedite%20appointments%20to%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20and%20also%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmechanism%20agreed%20by%20the%20Parties%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Article%2017.2%20on%20Appellate%20Review%20in%20the%20WTO%E2%80%99s%20Dispute%20Settlement%20Understanding%20(DSU)%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20DSB%20(Dispute%20Settlement%20Body)%20shall%20appoint%20persons%20to%20serve%20on%20the%20Appellate%20Body%20for%20a%20four-year%20term%2C%20and%20each%20person%20may%20be%20reappointed%20once.%20However%2C%20the%20terms%20of%20three%20of%20the%20seven%20persons%20appointed%20immediately%20after%20the%20entry%20into%20force%20of%20the%20WTO%20Agreement%20shall%20expire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20two%20years%2C%20to%20be%20determined%20by%20lot.%20Vacancies%20shall%20be%20filled%20as%20they%20arise.%20A%20person%20appointed%20to%20replace%20a%20person%20whose%20term%20of%20office%20has%20not%20expired%20shall%20hold%20office%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20predecessor%E2%80%99s%20term.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20under%20the%20%E2%80%9Cscope%20of%20appeal%2Freview%20mechanism%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20facilitator%E2%80%99s%20Yellow%20Box%2C%20the%20US%20proposed%20that%20the%20new%20Appellate%20Body%20would%20agree%20to%20the%20following%20conditions%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELimited%20to%20issues%20of%20law%20covered%20in%20the%20panel%20report%20and%20legal%20interpretation%20developed%20by%20the%20panel%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStandard%20of%20review%20for%20questions%20of%20law%2C%20under%20which%20an%20appellant%20must%20establish%20that%20the%20panel%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cna.%20Was%20guilty%20of%20gross%20misconduct%2C%20bias%2C%20or%20serious%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20or%20otherwise%20materially%20violated%20a%20rule%20of%20conduct%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cnb.%20Seriously%20departed%20from%20a%20fundamental%20rule%20of%20procedure%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cnc.%20Manifestly%20exceeded%20its%20powers%2C%20authority%2C%20or%20jurisdiction%2C%20and%20any%20of%20these%20acts%20by%20the%20panel%20materially%20affected%20the%20decision%20and%20threatens%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20G20%20trade%20ministers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20is%20going%20to%20be%20assessed%20for%20what%20the%20trade%20ministers%20would%20have%20to%20say%20on%20the%20US%E2%80%99%20bulldozer%20efforts%20on%20the%20critical%20dispute%20settlement%20WTO%20reform%2C%20including%20on%20the%20strength%2C%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%20of%20the%20two-tier%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBulldozer%20on%20Paris%20Climate%20Change%20Agreement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20EU%20have%20gone%20against%20their%20Paris%20commitments%20of%20providing%20climate%20finance%20and%20technology%20to%20developing%20countries.%20While%20the%20%24100%20billion%20financial%20commitment%20remains%20unfulfilled%2C%20the%20EU%20has%20imposed%20a%20carbon%20border%20adjustment%20mechanism%20(CBAM)%20on%20its%20imports%20which%20will%20not%20only%20adversely%20impact%20the%20exports%20from%20developing%20countries%20but%20also%20lead%20to%20disproportionate%20changes%20in%20global%20real%20incomes%20with%20advanced%20countries%E2%80%99%20real%20income%20increasing%20by%20%242.5%20billion%20and%20developing%20countries%E2%80%99%20real%20income%20falling%20by%20%245.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20United%20Nations%20Conference%20on%20Trade%20and%20Development%20(UNCTD)%20finds%20that%20CBAM%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20global%20carbon%20emissions%20by%20only%200.1%25.%20Other%20advanced%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20are%20also%20discussing%20the%20imposition%20of%20CBAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20say%20the%20G20%20meetings%20for%20various%20chapters%20at%20colossal%20expenditure%20to%20the%20exchequer%20may%20seem%20like%20Emperor%E2%80%99s%20new%20clothes%20without%20any%20outcome%20worth%20the%20name%20for%20posterity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fravi-kanth-devarakonda%5C%22%3ERavi%20Kanth%20Devarakonda%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692090205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwill-the-g20-stand-against-the-bulldozer-tactics-deployed-by-the-us-to-weaken-wto%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20seems%20determined%20to%20decimate%20the%20two-tier%20dispute%20settlement%20system%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20trade%20ministerial