n's%20and%20Temu's.%20My%20Shein%20order%20totaled%20%2432.24%20after%20receiving%20free%20shipping%20and%20a%20%2410%20discount%20that%20was%20automatically%20added%20to%20my%20cart.%20This%20didn't%20seem%20too%20expensive%20or%20too%20cheap%20for%20the%20three%20items%20I%20purchased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20on%20Temu%20were%20so%20low%20that%20I%20was%20worried%20the%20products%20would%20be%20terrible%20quality.%20I'd%20added%20five%20additional%20items%20to%20my%20cart%2C%20including%20a%20two-piece%20lounge%20set%20and%20three%20sets%20of%20press-on%20nails%2C%20and%20the%20subtotal%20came%20to%20%2454.24.%20But%20with%20additional%20discounts%20the%20app%20added%20at%20checkout%2C%20I%20paid%20%2428.11%20and%20received%20free%20shipping.%20It%20didn't%20make%20sense%20how%20I%20purchased%20more%20items%20but%20spent%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFastest%20Shipping%3A%20Amazon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223765%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22flat%20lay%20image%20of%20Amazon%20package%2C%20pink%20heels%2C%20checkered%20pants%2C%20and%20a%20claw%20clip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da3f211f51cc001968e336%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222824%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20disappointed%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20products%20I%20purchased%20from%20Amazon%2C%20since%20it%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20of%20the%20three%20online%20retailers.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20placed%20all%20three%20orders%20on%20July%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20received%20my%20Amazon%20orders%20first%2C%20on%20July%2021%20and%2022.%20Each%20item%20shipped%20separately.%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20annoyed%20that%20the%20shoes%20were%20shipped%20in%20a%20flimsy%20bag%20instead%20of%20a%20box%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20getting%20crushed%20in%20transit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20received%20my%20Shein%20order%20a%20