31%2Cimgsize-13698.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fone-dead-in-a-russian-military-jet-trainer-crash-in-a-region-near-crimea%2Farticleshow%2F102744788.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102744788.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOne%20person%20was%20killed%20when%20a%20Russian%20military%20jet%20trainer%20crashed%20while%20attempting%20to%20land%20in%20a%20region%20bordering%20Russia-annexed%20Crimea%2C%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%20said%20Monday.%20The%20crash%20of%20the%20Czechoslovak-made%20L-39%20in%20the%20Krasnodar%20region%20was%20the%20second%20fatal%20military%20crash%20on%20a%20training%20flight%20in%20three%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fone-dead-in-a-russian-military-jet-trainer-crash-in-a-region-near-crimea%2Farticleshow%2F102744788.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fone-dead-in-a-russian-military-jet-trainer-crash-in-a-region-near-crimea%2Famp_articleshow%2F102744788.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fone-dead-in-a-russian-military-jet-trainer-crash-in-a-region-near-crimea%2Famp_articleshow%2F102744788.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Big%20OBC%20Outreach%2C%20PM%20Announces%20Scheme%20To%20Help%20Traditional%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20outreach%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20next%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20announced%20a%20scheme%20to%20help%20those%20earning%20a%20living%20through%20traditional%20skills.%20The%20scheme%20will%20have%20an%20allocation%20of%20Rs%2013%2C000-Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20of%20blunting%20the%20opposition's%20efforts%20to%20attract%20the%20OBC%20vote%20through%20moves%20like%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20which%20is%20being%20planned%20in%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20announced%20the%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20and%20said%20the%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20helping%20those%20with%20traditional%20skills%2C%20who%20use%20their%20hands%20and%20basic%20tools%20to%20make%20a%20living.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20largely%20from%20the%20OBC%20sections.%20They%20can%20be%20people%20like%20carpenters%2C%20goldsmiths%2C%20masons%2C%20washermen%20and%20women%2C%20and%20barbers.%20To%20give%20such%20workers%20strength%2C%20we%20will%20launch%20Vishwakarma%20Yojana%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Vishwakarma%20Jayanti%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwakarma%20Jayanti%2C%20which%20will%20be%20celebrated%20on%20September%2017%20this%20year%2C%20sees%20prayer%20events%20being%20organised%20across%20the%20country%20to%20worship%20the%20deity%20of%20craftsmen%20and%20architects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20resolution%20at%20the%20second%20mega%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20demand%20a%20fair%20hearing%20for%20all%20socially%2C%20educationally%20and%20economically%20backward%20communities%3B%20and%2C%20as%20a%20first%20step%2C%20implement%20the%20caste%20census.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court%20had%20dismissed%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20Bihar%20government's%20decision%20to%20conduct%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20and%20the%20socio-economic%20survey%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20also%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20caste%20census%20but%20said%20it%20will%20hear%20the%20petitions%20against%20it%20on%20August%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20contended%20that%20the%20Bihar%20government%20cannot%20conduct%20the%20census%20as%20it%20violates%20a%20constitutional%20mandate%2C%20which%20states%20that%20such%20exercises%20can%20only%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20Centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20after%20its%20formation%2C%20the%20Justice%20G%20Rohini-headed%20Commission%20for%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBC%20groups%20has%20also%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20July%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OBC%20vote%20will%20also%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20this%20year%2C%20especially%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20a%20high%20population%20of%20people%20from%20these%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692088620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F17alfef_pm-modi-red-fort-650_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20major%20outreach%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20next%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20announced%20a%20scheme%20to%20help%20those%20earning%20a%20living%20through%20traditional%20skills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-big-obc-outreach-pm-announces-scheme-to-help-traditional-workers-4299623%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20To%20Mission%202047%3A%20PM%20Modi's%2015%20Mantras%20In%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%2010th%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20Red%20Fort%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20laid%20down%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20country's%20development%20and%20his%20government's%20plan%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%2015%20mantras%20in%20his%2090-minute%20speech%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAmrit%20kaal%20is%20Kartavya%20Kaal%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day%20that%20marked%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20government's%20Azadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%20to%20mark%2075%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20equated%20Amrit%20kaal%20with%20Kartavya%20kaal%20--%20meaning%20the%20%26quot%3Btime%20of%20duty%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20the%20decision%20of%20today%20will%20bear%20fruit%20over%201%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMission%202047%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20a%20target%20of%202047%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20next%20five%20years%20will%20be%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20country's%20aspirations%20are%20met%20by%20the%20time%20it%20celebrates%20100%20years%20of%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDemography%2C%20Democracy%2C%20Diversity%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20underlined%20how%20India's%20demographic%20strength%2C%20coupled%20with%20its%20democracy%20and%20diversity%2C%20can%20help%20power%20its%20development%20journey.%20The%20convergence%20of%20these%20three%20can%20fulfill%20the%20country's%20dreams%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNation%20First%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20putting%20the%20nation%20first%20forms%20the%20basis%20of%20every%20decision%20of%20his%20government.%20The%20centre%2C%20he%20says%2C%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20single%20penny%20of%20taxpayers'%20money%20is%20used%20for%20their%20welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMission%20Against%20%26quot%3B3%20Evils%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20Opposition%20forces%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20country's%20mission%20should%20be%20to%20eradicate%20the%20evils%20of%20corruption%2C%20dynasty%20and%20appeasement%20which%20he%20said%20will%20be%20hurdles%20to%20its%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20Guarantees%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20spelt%20out%20three%20guarantees%20-%20to%20ensure%20India%20is%20among%20the%20country's%20top%20three%20economies%2C%20easy%20loans%20for%20building%20homes%20and%2025%2C000%20Jan%20Aushadhi%20Kendras%20for%20medicines%20at%20low%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B2%20Crore%20Lakhpati%20Didi%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20the%20role%20of%20women%20self-help%20groups%20in%20taking%20development%20and%20welfare%20measures%20to%20remote%20corners%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20now%20his%20goal%20to%20make%20%26quot%3B2%20crore%20lakhpati%20didis%26quot%3B%20by%20empowering%20women.%20He%20said%20the%20government%20will%20take%20steps%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPolicy%20Clear%2C%20Intent%20Clean%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20has%20its%20policies%20clear%20and%20its%20intent%20clean%20to%20ensure%20all-round%20development.%20Only%20a%20policy%20of%20ensuring%20everyone's%20well-being%20can%20help%20us%20become%20a%20developed%20nation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmphasis%20on%20Regional%20Languages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20centre%20is%20taking%20steps%20to%20ensure%20higher%20studies%20in%20regional%20languages.%20He%20thanked%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20its%20steps%20to%20make%20operative%20part%20of%20judgments%20available%20in%20regional%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BSolution%20Through%20Peace%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20today%20started%20his%20speech%20by%20assuring%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20unrest%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20150%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20The%20centre%20and%20state%20government%20are%20working%20to%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Cooperation%20To%20Collaboration%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20his%20government%20has%20already%20set%20up%20a%20Ministry%20for%20Cooperation%20and%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20further%20build%20on%20its%20efforts%2C%20to%20make%20a%20gradual%20movement%20from%20cooperation%20to%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVishwakarma%20Yojana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20will%20launch%20a%20'Vishwakarma%20Yojana'%20next%20month%20with%20an%20allocation%20of%20at%20least%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20for%20those%20with%20traditional%20skills.%20This%20scheme%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20focus%20on%20skilled%20workers%20such%20as%20barbers%2C%20goldsmiths%20and%20washermen%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BOne%20Earth%2C%20One%20Family%2C%20One%20Future%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20how%20India%20helped%20out%20other%20countries%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20the%20world's%20friend%20who%20does%20not%20think%20just%20about%20itself.%20After%20Covid%2C%20India%20advocated%20for%20'One%20Earth%2C%20One%20Health'%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Promise%20For%20Next%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20said%20people%20gave%20him%20an%20opportunity%20in%202014%2C%20reposed%20their%20trust%20in%202019%20and%20if%20the%20people's%20blessings%20are%20with%20him%2C%20he%20would%20return%20to%20Red%20Fort%20and%20address%20the%20nation%20next%20year%20too.%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20due%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BEmbrace%20Challenges%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20shared%20a%20short%20poem.%20The%20lines%20laid%20down%20his%20government's%20plan%20for%20the%20country%20and%20exhorted%20it%20to%20embrace%20challenges%20and%20make%20India%20prominent%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692088320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F1ome7nlg_pm-modi_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependence-day-updates-independence-day-pm-narendra-modi-plans-promises-poetry-pm-modis-15-mantras-in-independence-day-speech-4299519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%2010th%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20Red%20Fort%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20laid%20down%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20country's%20development%20and%20his%20government's%20plan%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependence-day-updates-independence-day-pm-narendra-modi-plans-promises-poetry-pm-modis-15-mantras-in-independence-day-speech-4299519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependence-day-updates-independence-day-pm-narendra-modi-plans-promises-poetry-pm-