nts%20celebrating%20India's%2077th%20Independence%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Dr%20Prabhuram%20Choudhary%20was%20on%20a%20stage%20in%20Raisen%20to%20receive%20the%20salute%20during%20a%20march%20past%20when%20he%20collapsed.%20Officials%20present%20at%20the%20event%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20his%20rescue%20and%20shifted%20him%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%20in%20Raisen.%20Dr%20Choudhary%20was%20examined%20by%20doctors%20who%20said%20he%20is%20currently%20under%20observation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20in%20Mauganj%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Girish%20Gautam%20hoisted%20the%20flag%20but%20his%20health%20suddenly%20deteriorated%20as%20he%20began%20addressing%20the%20public.%20The%20doctors%20were%20immediately%20called%20in%20and%20he%20is%20said%20to%20be%20undergoing%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day%2C%20three%20different%20tricolor%20rallies%20were%20organised%20in%20Raisen%20under%20the%20Har%20Ghar%20Tiranga%20Abhiyan.%20The%20rallies%20were%20attended%20by%20school%20children%2C%20police%20and%20administration%20officials%2C%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20Tiranga%20Yatra%20was%20also%20taken%20out%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Dr%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20appeared%20healthy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Choudhary%20extended%20Independence%20Day%20greetings%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20country%20and%20urged%20everyone%20to%20hoist%20the%20tricolor%20at%20their%20respective%20homes%20and%20celebrate%20the%20occasion%20with%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692086040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ffsj1307o_prabhuram-choudhary-_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F77th-independence-day-madhya-pradesh-minister-dr-prabhuram-choudhary-collapses-on-stage-during-independence-day-parade-4299562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Health%20Minister%20and%20the%20Assembly%20Speaker%20collapsed%20on%20stage%20at%20two%20separate%20events%20celebrating%20India's%2077th%20Independence%20Day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F77th-independence-day-madhya-pradesh-minister-dr-prabhuram-choudhary-collapses-on-stage-during-independence-day-parade-4299562%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F77th-independence-day-madhya-pradesh-minister-dr-prabhuram-choudhary-collapses-on-stage-during-independence-day-parade-4299562%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F77th-independence-day-madhya-pradesh-minister-dr-prabhuram-choudhary-collapses-on-stage-during-independence-day-parade-4299562%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice's%20%5C%22Demolition%2C%20Arbitrary%20Arrest%5C%22%20Remark%20On%20Judiciary's%20Role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%2C%20soon%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-indias-folded-hands-gesture-on-pms-language-remark-4299123%5C%22%3Epraise%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20judiciary's%20efforts%20to%20translate%20its%20key%20judgments%20into%20regional%20languages%2C%20made%20a%20reference%20to%20arbitrary%20arrests%20and%20threatened%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20specifying%20any%20case%2C%20the%20CJI%2C%20while%20addressing%20his%20colleagues%20at%20an%20Independence%20Day%20event%20at%20the%20top%20court%20premises%2C%20said%20that%20irrespective%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20case%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20system%20is%20to%20grant%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20sense%20of%20confidence%20in%20an%20individual%20that%20an%20arbitrary%20arrest%2C%20a%20threatened%20demolition%2C%20if%20their%20properties%20are%20attached%20unlawfully%2C%20must%20find%20solace%20and%20a%20voice%20in%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20with%20Union%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20present%20on%20stage%20as%20special%20guest%20at%20the%20event%20organised%20by%20the%C2%A0Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%2076%20years%20suggests%20that%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20judiciary%20is%20the%20history%20of%20struggle%20of%20daily%20common%20people%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20judiciary%20is%20to%20eliminate%20the%20barriers%20of%20access%20to%20justice%20and%20have%20a%20roadmap%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20the%20judiciary%20is%20accessible%20and%20inclusive%20to%20the%20last%20person%20in%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20judge%20also%20assured%20his%20colleagues%20that%20every%20complaint%2C%20each%20letter%20to%20him%2C%20and%20even%20addressed%20to%20social%20media%20instead%20of%20him%2C%20is%20dealt%20with%20by%20him%20personally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20request%20lawyers%2C%20if%20you%20have%20any%20grievance%20do%20not%20run%20outside%20the%20court%2C%20you%20have%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family%20sitting%20here%20to%20address%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Master%20of%20the%20Roster%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20institutions%20such%20as%20the%20media%2C%20bureaucracy%2C%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20voluntary%20organisations%20have%20an%20important%20role%20in%20bringing%20development%20to%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20our%20founding%20leaders%20set%20the%20national%20priorities%20and%20visualised%20the%20institutional%20apparatus%20to%20bring%20out%20social%2C%20political%2C%20and%20economic%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2076%20years%2C%20our%20tricolour%20flutters%20in%20the%20winds%20of%20liberty%20and%20equality.%20There%20are%20times%20when%20the%20wind%20has%20stood%20still%20and%20there%20have%20been%20storms%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20but%20the%20flag%20serves%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20our%20collective%20heritage%20and%20guides%20us%20towards%20our%20future%20aspirations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20will%20expand%20its%20infrastructure%20to%20add%2027%20additional%20courtrooms%2C%204%20registrar%20courtrooms%2C%20and%20more%20facilities%20for%20lawyers%20and%20litigants%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20revealed%20that%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20overhaul%20judicial%20infrastructure%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20planning%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20building%20to%20accommodate%20additional%20courtrooms%20and%20other%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692085980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fgjf3appg_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_15_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justices-demolition-arbitrary-arrest-remark-on-judiciarys-role-4299483%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThat%20sense%20of%20confidence%20in%20an%20individual%20that%20an%20arbitrary%20arrest%2C%20a%20threatened%20demolition%2C%20if%20their%20properties%20are%20attached%20unlawfully%2C%20must%20find%20solace%20and%20a%20voice%20in%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justices-demolition-arbitrary-arrest-remark-on-judiciarys-role-4299483%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justices-demolition-arbitrary-arrest-remark-on-judiciarys-role-4299483%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-jus