and%20the%20second%20is%20the%20utter%20devotion%20with%20which%20it%20remembers%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20independence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20first%20comes%20out%20clearly%20in%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20obsessive%20worship%20of%20the%20national%20flag%20%E2%80%93%20punishing%20all%20and%20sundry%20for%20%E2%80%98disrespecting%E2%80%99%20the%20sacred%20tricolour%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20this%20extra-religiosity%20is%20actually%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20utter%20contempt%20with%20which%20their%20political%20ancestors%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%2C%20had%20opposed%20our%20tricolour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20Right%20had%20taken%20no%20part%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20freedom%20and%20while%20the%20RSS%20had%20kept%20its%20members%20away%20from%20it%20all%2C%20the%20other%20organisation%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20of%20Savarkar%20and%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee%2C%20had%20sided%20with%20British%20imperial%20rule.%20This%20was%20particularly%20cruel%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%20of%201942%2C%20as%20the%20British%20were%20then%20jailing%20thousands%20of%20Indian%20freedom%20fighters%20and%20mercilessly%20beating%20up%20others.%20Both%20the%20present%20regime%E2%80%99s%20programmes%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20ultra-veneration%20of%20the%20national%20flag%20(introducing%20a%20non-Hindu%20whip%20of%20%E2%80%98blasphemy%E2%80%99%20around%20it)%20and%20the%20national%20celebration%20of%20the%2075th%20year%20of%20Independence%20are%20really%20meant%20to%20smother%20over%20the%20ugly%20reality%20of%20history.%20They%20represent%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20appropriate%20the%20wreath%20of%20patriotism%20and%20the%20glory%20that%20accompanies%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20mouthpiece%2C%20Organiser%2C%20had%20declared%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20path%20in%20its%20issues%20of%2017%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3End%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20July%201947.%20It%20stated%20that%20the%20Indian%20national%20tricolour%20will%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20be%20respected%20and%20owned%20by%20the%20Hindus.%20The%20word%20three%20is%20in%20itself%20an%20evil%2C%20and%20a%20flag%20having%20three%20colours%20will%20certainly%20produce%20a%20very%20bad%20psychological%20effect%20and%20is%20injurious%20to%20a%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fveer-savarkar-the-staunchest-advocate-of-loyalty-to-the-english-government%5C%22%3EHow%20Did%20Savarkar%2C%20a%20Staunch%20Supporter%20of%20British%20Colonialism%2C%20Come%20to%20Be%20Known%20as%20%E2%80%98Veer%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20this%20logic%2C%20the%20trinity%20of%20%3Cem%3EBrahma%2C%20Vishnu%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20Maheshwar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20is%20integral%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20would%20become%20unacceptable%20and%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETriGuna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20virtues%20expounded%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagavat%20Gita%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eare%20to%20be%20rejected.%20Will%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Et%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erishul%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20is%20based%20on%20three%2C%20hence%20be%20%E2%80%98evil%E2%80%99%3F%20In%20his%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBunch%20of%20Thoughts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20MS%20Golwalkar%2C%20the%20second%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarsanghchalak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20head%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20had%20expressed%20his%20opposition%20to%20free%20India%E2%80%99s%20flag.%20%E2%80%9COur%20leaders%20have%20set%20up%20a%20new%20flag%20for%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20why%20did%20they%20do%20so%3F%E2%80%A6%20%E2%80%A6.Ours%20is%20an%20ancient%20and%20great%20nation%20with%20a%20glorious%20past.%20Then%2C%20had%20we%20no%20flag%20of%20our%20own%3F%20Had%20we%20no%20national%20emblem%20at%20all%20these%20thousands%20of%20years%3F%20Undoubtedly%20we%20had.%20Then%20why%20this%20utter%20void%2C%20this%20utter%20vacuum%20in%20our%20minds%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20Golwalkar%20was%20hinting%20at%20as%20our%20%E2%80%98ancient%20flag%E2%80%99%20or%20national%20emblem%20of%20India%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3EBhagwa%20Dhwaj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20saffron%20%E2%80%98split%20flag%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20a%20purely%20Hindu%20flag%20and%20he%20overlooked%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20national%20tricolour%20represents%20the%20plurality%20of%20Indian%20civilisation.%20The%20point%20is%20that%20the%20RSS%20had%20opposed%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20had%20continued%20to%20do%20so%20until%20the%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel%2C%20kept%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20jail%20for%2018%20months%2C%20from%20February%201948%2C%20following%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%20As%20a%20condition%20for%20the%20release%20of%20their%20leaders%20in%20July%201949%2C%20the%20RSS%20swore%20to%20respect%20the%20Indian%20flag.%20It%20is%20ironic%20to%20see%20how%20strongmen%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20threaten%20and%20beat%20up%20hapless%20citizens%20who%20they%20view%20as%20not%20giving%20sufficient%20honour%20to%20the%20tricolour.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20we%20commemorate%20the%2081st%20anniversary%20of%20the%20historic%20Quit%20India%20movement%2C%20we%20are%20reminded%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20boycotted%20the%20most%20momentous%20phase%20of%20our%20national%20struggle.%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20is%20venerated%20by%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20for%20switching%20from%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20to%20establish%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20incarnation%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20went%20a%20step%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Frss-hindutva-nationalism%5C%22%3EHistory%20Shows%20How%20Patriotic%20the%20RSS%20Really%20Is%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20largest%20party%20that%20emerged%20from%20the%201937%20elections%2C%20refused%20to%20support%20AK%20Fazlul%20Haq%E2%80%99s%20first%20coalition%20cabinet%20in%20the%20undivided%20Bengal%20Province%2C%20Mookerjee%20spied%20an%20opportunity%20to%20become%20a%20minister%20under%20Haq.%20He%20soon%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20British%20for%20both%20blessings%20and%20power%2C%20as%20the%20governor%20had%20an%20overriding%20role%20under%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constitutionofindia.net%2Fhistorical-constitution%2Fgovernment-of-india-act-1935%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%201935%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20colonial%20government%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20less%20for%20such%20overtures%20but%20then%2C%20he%20sensed%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20nervousness%20when%20the%20Congress%20became%20more%20and%20more%20aggressive%20in%20the%20middle%20of%201942%20%E2%80%94%20a%20few%20weeks%20from%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Do%20or%20Die%E2%80%99%20Quit%20India%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20when%20he%20wrote%20his%20terribly%20controversial%20letter%20to%20the%20governor%20of%20Bengal%2C%20John%20Herbert%2C%20on%20the%2026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20July%201942.%20He%20condemned%20the%20national%20movement%20declaring%20%E2%80%9Canybody%20who%2C%20during%20the%20war%2C%20plans%20to%20stir%20up%20mass%20feelings%2C%20resulting%20in%20internal%20disturbances%20or%20insecurity%2C%20must%20be%20resisted%20by.%E2%80%A6government%E2%80%9D.%20To%20ingratiate%20himself%20to%20foreign%20rulers%20and%20to%20create%20hurdles%20for%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20anti-British%20agitation%2C%20Mookerjee%20approached%20the%20governor%20saying%20%E2%80%9Cas%20one%20of%20your%20Ministers%2C%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20offer%20you%20my%20whole-hearted%20cooperation%20and%20serve%20my%20province%20and%20country%20at%20this%20hour%20of%20crisis%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20leader%2C%20VD%20Savarkar%2C%20had%20earlier%20set%20such%20supplicatory%20traditions%2C%20by%20begging%20the%20British%20for%20mercy%20for%20being%20released%20from%20jail.%20Shyama%20Prasad%20followed%20this%20and%20told%20governor%20Herbert%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20of%20the%20Bengal%20province%20should%20be%20carried%20on%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20best%20efforts%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20this%20(Quit%20India)%20movement%20will%20fail%E2%80%9D.%20He%20promised%20the%20governor%20that%20he%20and%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20ministers%20would%20%E2%80%9Ctell%20the%20public%20that%20the%20freedom%20for%20which%20the%20Congress%20has%20started%20the%20movement%2C%20already%20belongs%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%A6Indians%20have%20to%20trust%20the%20British%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20tradition%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20political%20gurus%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20personally%20renamed%20the%20Kolkata%20Port%20Trust%20after%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee.%20Governor%20Herbert%20was%20not%20impressed%20by%20this%20crouching%20minister%20and%20this%20antagonised%20Mookerjee%2C%20who%20started%20complaining%20against%20him%20and%20his%20bureaucrats.%20It%20is%20this%20later%20angst%20that%20is%20bandied%20around%20by%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20to%20justify%20that%20Mookerjee%20was%20actually%20a%20%E2%80%98nationalist%E2%80%99.%20The%20Hindu%20Right%20family%20has%20not%20found%20time%20to%20apologise%20for%20opposing%20both%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20the%20national%20struggle.%20It%20is%20upto%20the%20nation%20whether%20to%20consider%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fixation%20with%20the%20tricolour%20and%20his%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%20as%20either%20atonement%20for%20past%20misdeeds%20of%20his%20gurus%20or%20as%20attempts%20to%20snatch%20the%20monopoly%20of%20patriotism%20and%20obliterate%20facts%20and%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawhar-sircar%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawhar-sircar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EJawhar%20Sircar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20He%20has%20been%20culture%20secretary%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20CEO%20of%20Prasar%20Bharati.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692079787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15112516%2Fimg_2622-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-the-hindu-right-opposed-the-national-flag-and-the-quit-india-movement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%2C%20the%20RSS's%20mouthpiece%2C%20Organiser%2C%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20national%20flag%20would%20never%20be%20respected%20by%20the%20Hindus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-the-hindu-right-opposed-the-national-flag-and-the-quit-india-movement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20address%20nation%20from%20Red%2