ng%20suspended%2C%20he%20said.%20My%20own%20mike%20has%20been%20muted%20in%20the%20house%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F77th-independence-day-celebrations-today-pm-to-address-nation-10-points-4298679%5C%22%3EPM's%2090-minute%20long%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%2C%20he%20said%20an%20impression%20has%20been%20created%20that%20developmental%20work%20has%20taken%20place%20only%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20recounted%20the%20role%20of%20former%20Congress%20PMs%20and%20their%20contribution%20towards%20nation%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20an%20attack%20on%20some%20salient%20characteristics%20of%20our%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20first%2C%20in%20many%20decades%2C%20that%20a%20Congress%20president%20has%20attacked%20the%20government%20on%20Independence%20Day.%20Avoiding%20any%20criticism%20or%20attack%20on%20the%20Centre%20on%20Independence%20Day%20has%20so%20far%20been%20a%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20chair%20with%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20name%20was%20among%20the%20vacant%20seats%20at%20a%20section%20of%20the%20historic%20Red%20Fort%20where%20PM%20Modi%20delivered%20his%20speech.%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20Red%20Fort%20for%20the%20speech%20as%20he%20had%20an%20eye%20problem.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20also%20expected%20to%20hoist%20the%20flag%20in%20his%20own%20house%2C%20then%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20office%2C%20and%20with%20so%20much%20security%20for%20the%20PM%20and%20others%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20allow%20him%20to%20leave%20till%20the%20Home%20Minister%2C%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20Speaker%2C%20and%20some%20others%20did%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20impossible%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20called%20Bharat%20Mata%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20e