https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbeyonce-lizzo-shoutout-renaissance-concert-atlanta-lawsuit-1235696546%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbeyonce-lizzo-shoutout-renaissance-concert-atlanta-lawsuit-1235696546%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR's%20Gift%20To%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20has%20announced%20full%20waiver%20of%20farmer%20loans%20upto%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20to%20fulfill%20the%20promise%20he%20made%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20state%20elections%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20farmers%20who%20took%20loan%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20will%20be%20freed%20from%20debt%20burden%20and%20has%20ordered%20to%20repay%20loan%20amount%20upto%20Rs%2099%2C999%20to%20the%20banks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Chief%20Secretary%20to%20Finance%2C%20Ramakrishna%20Rao%20issued%20instructions%20in%20this%20regard%20on%20Monday.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20money%20will%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20banks%20immediately%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20farmers.%20On%20the%20instructions%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%2C%20the%20finance%20department%20released%20Rs%205%2C809.78%20crore%20on%20behalf%20of%209%2C02%2C843%20farmers%20on%20Monday.%20The%20released%20amount%20will%20be%20deposited%20in%20the%20farmers%20accounts%20in%20the%20%C2%A0banks%20under%20loan%20waiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20loan%20waiver%20will%20be%20implemented%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%20He%20directed%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20Agriculture%20and%20Finance%20Department%20of%20the%20state%20to%20write%20to%20the%20banks%20and%20get%20comprehensive%20details.%20It%20took%20a%20year%20to%20complete%20the%20entire%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20lockdown%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20demonetisation%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20faced%20a%20big%20difficulty%20in%20mobilising%20the%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20has%20already%20paid%20Rs%201%2C943.64%20crore%20to%20the%20banks%20in%20respect%20of%207%2C19%2C488%20farmers%20who%20took%20loan%20up%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20This%20amount%20has%20been%20adjusted%20in%20loan%20waiver%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Rs%205%2C809.78%20crore%20have%20been%20released%20for%20the%20loan%20waiver%20of%20farmers%20who%20owe%20up%20to%20Rs%2099%2C999%20rupees%20to%20the%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%202nd%2C%20KCR%20held%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20on%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20and%20farmer%20loan%20waiver%20and%20announced%20that%20the%20farmer%20loan%20waiver%20scheme%20will%20be%20implemented.%20Clear%20instructions%20are%20given%20to%20the%20officials%20to%20complete%20the%20loan%20waiver%20process%20within%2045%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20T%20Harish%20Rao%20also%20issued%20a%20Budget%20Releasing%20Order%20(BRO)%20on%20August%203%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20release%20of%20loan%20waiver%20funds%20started%20on%20August%203rd%20.%20In%20accordance%20with%20the%20instructions%20given%20by%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20fresh%20orders%20have%20been%20issued%20%C2%A0to%20settle%20the%20debt%20amount%20up%20to%20Rs%2099%2C999.%20With%20the%20latest%20decision%2C%20a%20total%20of%2016%2C66%2C899%20farmers%20in%20the%20state%20will%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20day%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20reviewed%20and%20announced%20the%20farmers'%20loan%20waiver%20on%20August%202%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Harish%20Rao%20and%20Special%20Principal%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Finance%20Department%20Ramakrishna%20Rao%20chalked%20out%20a%2045-day%20action%20plan%20and%20executed%20the%20same.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20daily%20reviews%20and%20meetings%20with%20bankers%20are%20held%20to%20implement%20%C2%A0the%20loan%20waiver%20scheme%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%203rd%2C%20Rs%20237.85%20crore%20was%20released%20in%20respect%20of%2062%2C758%20farmers%20who%20took%20loans%20up%20to%20Rs%2041%2C000.%20Also%2C%20on%20August%204%2C%20Rs%20126.50%20crore%20loans%20were%20waived%20in%20respect%20of%2031%2C339%2039%20farmers%20whose%20loans%20are%20under%20Rs%2043%2C000%20and%20the%20funds%20were%20deposited%20in%20the%20bank%20accounts.%20The%20latest%20loan%20amounts%20up%20to%20Rs%2099%2C999%20are%20deposited.%20The%20number%20of%20farmers%20who%20owe%20up%20to%20Rs%2099%2C999%20is%209%2C02%2C843.%20The%20government%20will%20pay%20Rs%205809.78%20crore%20to%20the%20banks%20in%20this%20regard.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20government%20has%20paid%20Rs.%207753.43%20crore%20to%2016%2C66%2C899%20farmers%20under%20loan%20waiver%20scheme.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20prides%20itself%20on%20being%20farmer-friendly.%20Under%20Mission%20Kakatiya%2C%2035%2C000%20abandoned%20ponds%20and%20water%20bodies%20were%20repaired%20and%20a%20multi-purpose%20project%20Kaleshwaram%20was%20%C2%A0constructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20loan%20waiver%20scheme%20is%20said%20to%20have%20benefitted%2035%2C32%2C000%20%C2%A0farmers%20benefited.%20The%20government%20spent%20Rs%2016%2C144%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20Rs%207753.43%20crore%20farm%20loans%20have%20been%20waived%20benefitting%2016%2C%2066%2C899%20%C2%A0farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20also%20introduced%20the%20Rythu%20Bima%20Scheme%20to%20provide%20financial%20security%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20farmer%20in%20case%20of%20death%20due%20to%20any%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20premium%20amount%20is%20paid%20by%20the%20government.%201%2C08%2C051%20farmers%20who%20have%20died%20due%20to%20various%20reasons%20in%20the%20state%20have%20been%20supported%20till%20date.%20Rs%205%2C402.55%20crore%20insurance%20amount%20is%20paid%20to%20the%20bereaved%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%20also%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20only%20state%20in%20the%20country%20providing%2024%20hours%20free%20quality%20electricity%20to%20farmers.%20Free%20power%20is%20provided%20to%2027%2C49%2C000%20agricultural%20connections%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20the%20past%20nine%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20that%20has%20cost%20the%20government%20Rs%2096%2C288%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20says%20it%20has%20spent%20Rs%2032%2C700%20crores%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20basic%20facilities%20in%20the%20power%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20direct%20cash%20transfer%20scheme%2C%20meant%20to%20Finance%20agricultural%20inputs%20is%20Rythu%20Bandhu.%20The%20government%20says%2065%20lakh%20farmers%20have%20benefitted%20and%20Rs%2071%2C552%20crores%20has%20been%20deposited%20in%20the%20farmers'%20accounts%20in%2011%20installments%20%C2%A0so%20far%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692076320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fh8q25nso_k-chandrasekhar-rao-kcr_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fon-independence-day-telangana-chief-minister-kcrs-gift-to-farmers-4299182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20eve%20of%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20has%20announced%20full%20waiver%20of%20farmer%20loans%20upto%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20to%20fulfill%20the%20promise%20he%20made%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20state%20elections%20in%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fon-independence-day-telangana-chief-minister-kcrs-gift-to-farmers-4299182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fon-independence-day-telan