20with%20%E2%80%9CEk%20Bharat%2C%20Shreshtha%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20multiple%20laws%20on%20digitisation%20and%20the%20end%20of%20the%20digitisation%20process%20of%20Digital%20India%2C%20I%20must%20declare%20the%20death%20of%20independence%20of%20cyberspace%20as%20we%20know%20it%20for%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20360px)%2085vw%2C%20360px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22251%5C%22%3EWith%20continuous%20internet%20shutdowns%2C%20websites%20and%20application%20bans%2C%20mandatory%20Aadhaar%2C%20IT%20rules%20that%20censor%20anything%20online%2C%20facial%20recognition%20that%20powers%20active%20surveillance%2C%20VPN%20rules%20that%20want%20logs%20of%20all%20VPN%20servers%2C%20data%20raids%20on%20the%20media%20for%20phone%20cloning%20and%20a%20data%20protection%20law%20that%20forces%20duties%2C%20Digital%20India%20has%20run%20out%20of%20freedoms.%20Digital%20India%2C%20while%20wanting%20to%20become%20self-reliant%20and%20independent%20in%20the%20digitisation%20space%2C%20has%20entirely%20taken%20away%20citizens%E2%80%99%20freedoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20an%20independence%20for%20cyberspace%20comes%20from%20the%20early%20manifesto%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eff.org%2Fcyberspace-independence%5C%22%3EA%20Declaration%20of%20the%20Independence%20of%20Cyberspace%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20John%20Perry%20Barlow%2C%20a%20libertarian%20and%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Electronic%20Freedom%20Foundation.%20Barlow%20wrote%20this%20in%201996%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20dinner%20party%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20%E2%80%93%20the%20high%20table%20of%20Global%20Capital.%20Barlow%E2%80%99s%20simple%20message%20through%20the%20manifesto%20was%20%E2%80%9CGovernments%20can%E2%80%99t%20govern%20cyberspace%E2%80%9D.%20He%20declared%20cyberspace%E2%80%99s%20independence%20and%20claimed%20governments%20of%20the%20world%20have%20no%20sovereignty%20over%20cyberspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CGovernments%20of%20the%20Industrial%20World%2C%20you%20weary%20giants%20of%20flesh%20and%20steel%2C%20I%20come%20from%20Cyberspace%2C%20the%20new%20home%20of%20Mind.%20On%20behalf%20of%20the%20future%2C%20I%20ask%20you%20of%20the%20past%20to%20leave%20us%20alone.%20You%20are%20not%20welcome%20among%20us.%20You%20have%20no%20sovereignty%20where%20we%20gather.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarlow%E2%80%99s%20arguments%20were%20often%20misunderstood%2C%20if%20understood%20at%20all%2C%20with%20multiple%20commenters%20saying%20how%20Barlow%20was%20wrong.%20Twenty%20years%20after%20the%20manifesto%E2%80%99s%20release%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2016%2F02%2Fits-been-20-years-since-this-man-declared-cyberspace-independence%2F%5C%22%3Eclarified%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20dependence%20of%20cyberspace%20on%20physical%20infrastructure%20and%20how%20the%20government%20could%20intrude%20on%20cyberspace.%20But%20he%20clarified%20how%20the%20actors%20of%20cyberspace%20like%20himself%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20be%20governed%20and%20this%20marks%20up%20as%20an%20immune%20system%20that%20helps%20defend%20cyberspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ten%20Reasons%20Why%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Law%20Doesn't%20Empower%20Citizens%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-the-data-protection-law-empower-the-public%5C%22%3ETen%20Reasons%20Why%20The%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Law%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Empower%20Citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20internet%20was%20built%20on%20the%20ideas%20of%20anonymity%20and%20personal%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20with%20an%20aim%20of%20building%20a%20civilisation%20of%20mind.%20The%20early%20actors%20who%20were%20building%20the%20internet%20protocols%20actively%20strived%20to%20keep%20it%20away%20from%20corporations%20and%20nation%20states.%20The%20crypto%20wars%20between%20Cypherpunks%20and%20the%20United%20States%20government%20ensured%20encryption%20was%20available%20to%20the%20general%20public%20as%20the%20internet%20expanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20India%20does%20not%20have%20the%20same%20foundations%20of%20that%20of%20the%20early%20internet%2C%20with%20the%20Digital%20Identity%20Project%20%E2%80%93%20Aadhaar%20becoming%20its%20foundation.%20India%E2%80%99s%20digitisation%20process%20was%20based%20on%20ideas%20of%20identity%2C%20national%20sovereignty%20pushing%20surveillance%2C%20data%20as%20property%20and%20building%20India%20as%20an%20economic%20model.%20The%20nation%20state%20in%20this%20case%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20forced%20its%20ideas%20of%20property%2C%20expression%2C%20identity%20and%20movement%2C%20ideas%20that%20Barlow%20said%20do%20not%20apply%20for%20cyberspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20legal%20concepts%20of%20property%2C%20expression%2C%20identity%2C%20movement%2C%20and%20context%20do%20not%20apply%20to%20us.%20They%20are%20all%20based%20on%20matter%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20matter%20here.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20John%20Perry%20Barlow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20internet%20movements%2C%20which%20actively%20fought%20for%20freedoms%2C%20had%20their%20moments%20with%20the%20net%20neutrality%2C%20Section%2066A%2C%20right%20to%20privacy%20and%20internet%20shutdown%20judgements.%20But%20it%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20these%20freedoms%20exercised%20in%20India.%20Privacy%20has%20been%20overturned%20against%20people%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20share%20data%20everywhere.%20Even%20though%20Section%2066A%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%20has%20been%20scrapped%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20arrest%20activists%20and%20journalists%20like%20Disha%20Ravi%20and%20Mohammed%20Zubair%20under%20flimsy%20grounds.%20Manipur%20shows%20us%20yet%20again%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20remain%20a%20problem%20with%20no%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20other%20than%20pointing%20out%20the%20active%20censorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20democratic%20right%20that%20is%20being%20evolved%20for%20safeguarding%20citizens%20in%20Digital%20India%20has%20been%20completely%20overruled%20with%20laws%20and%20policies%20that%20have%20completely%20opposite%20effects.%20The%20early%20ideas%20of%20freedoms%20that%20were%20promoted%20through%20the%20internet%20and%20democratic%20participation%20that%20were%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20cornerstone%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20mere%20words.%20The%20economic%20and%20political%20factors%20that%20allow%20this%20to%20foster%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20might%20be%20hard%20to%20change%2C%20when%20it%20is%20being%20sold%20to%20the%20population%20as%20a%20success%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Personal%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20claims%20it%20has%20provided%20Indians%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20exercise%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20privacy.%C2%A0%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20full%20of%20exceptions%20that%20suppress%20our%20freedoms.%20In%20our%20post-truth%20world%2C%20there%20are%20now%20claims%20by%20the%20right%20wing%20crediting%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20electronics%20and%20information%20technology%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekar%20as%20the%20main%20player%20behind%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%20judgment%20and%20now%20the%20hero%20of%20the%20data%20protection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Who%20Are%20the%20Forces%20Shaping%20India's%20Data%20Push%20in%20Healthcare%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fhealth-ids-personal-data-privacy-india%5C%22%3EWho%20Are%20the%20Forces%20Shaping%20India%E2%80%99s%20Data%20Push%20in%20Healthcare%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20for%20ideas%20of%20borders%20and%20boundaries%20to%20cyberspace%20is%20now%20expanding%20to%20infrastructures%20with%20restrictions%20on%20electronic%20items%20like%20laptops.%20A%20self-resilient%20India%20with%20manufacturing%20carried%20out%20in%20India%20will%20have%20its%20own%20restrictions%20placed%20on%20electronics.%20A%20future%20with%20restrictions%20on%20encryption%20hardware%20is%20quite%20possible%2C%20denying%20Indians%20the%20ability%20to%20encrypt%20storage.%20We%20already%20witness%20this%20with%20the%20policies%20and%20arguments%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20makes%20in%20relation%20to%20WhatsApp%E2%80%99s%20encryption%20ability%20in%20our%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20take%20control%20of%20cyberspace%20and%20all%20forms%20of%20communications%20is%20a%20witch%20hunt%20that%20began%20after%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%20The%20security%20state%20interests%20of%20documenting%20everyone%20inside%20our%20borders%20is%20clearly%20visible%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-east-india%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-starts-capturing-biometric-data-of-illegal-immigrants-from-myanmar-8866925%2F%5C%22%3Epush%20to%20collect%20biometrics%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20push%20for%20biometrics-based%20infrastructure%20to%20regulate%20population%20travel%20is%20again%20visible%20with%20Digiyatra.%20These%20interests%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20areas%20with%20violence%20but%20to%20peaceful%20neighbourhoods%20where%20the%20police%20have%20pushed%20active%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20national%20sovereignty%20taking%20over%20above%20all%20else%20including%20personal%20freedoms%20has%20turned%20freedoms%20into%20mere%20slogans.%20This%20is%20not%20specific%20to%20cyberspace%2C%20but%20to%20all%20forms%20of%20fundamental%20rights%20that%20are%20being%20ignored%20by%20the%20nation%20state%20in%20its%20push%20for%20economic%20and%20political%20control.%20The%20idea%20of%20independence%20and%20freedoms%20don%E2%80%99t%20hold%20the%20same%20value%20with%20them%20being%20replaced%20with%20ideas%20of%20self-reliance%20and%20economic%20prosperity%20of%20the%20nation.%20I%20doubt%20if%20Indians%20can%20aspire%20for%20freedoms%20in%20cyberspace%2C%20given%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20the%20nation%20state%20takes%20over%20every%20aspect%20of%20our%20lives%20with%20digitisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692075548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15102624%2FDigital_India_poster_anti_caa_nrc_shaheeh_bagh_7_jan_2020.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdigital-india-has-run-out-of-freedoms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20democratic%20right%20that%20is%20being%20evolved%20for%20safeguarding%20citizens%20in%20Digital%20India%20has%20been%20overruled%20by%20laws%20and%20policies%20that%20have%20completely%20opposite%20effects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fdigital-india-has-run-out-of-freedoms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Captain%20Pandya%20%5C%22Work%20In%20Progress%5C%22%2C%20Batter%20Pandya%20'Needs%20Runs'%3A%20Ex-Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20India's%203-2%20loss%20to%20West%20indies%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20T20I%20series%2C%20former%20wicketk