023-08-15-at-9.53.59-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20his%20tenth%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%20and%20the%20last%20one%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20in%20Hindi%20about%20attacks%20on%20the%20country%20%E2%80%9C1%2C200%20years%20ago%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20invoking%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20oft-repeated%20claim%20that%20India%20under%20Mughal%20rule%20did%20not%20have%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20did%20not%20know%20then%20that%20one%20incident%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20defeat%20of%20a%20king%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20another%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20ensnare%20India%20in%20a%201000-year%20slavery%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20renewed%20the%20pitch%20for%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20tirade%20against%20Mughal%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20effect%20Muslim%20%E2%80%93%20rule%2C%20by%20saying%20that%20India%20continued%20to%20be%20stuck%20in%20slavery%20for%20years%20afterwards.%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20wanted%20to%20looted%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20was%20small%2C%20but%20it%20left%20an%20impression%20for%201%2C000%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20an%20opportunity%20again%2C%20Modi%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20lucky%20that%20we%20are%20in%20this%20first%20year%20of%20Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%A6mark%20my%20words%2C%20what%20we%20do%20in%20this%20time%20will%20go%20into%20making%20the%20next%201%2C000%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinutes%20later%2C%20Modi%20said%20India%20now%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdemography%2C%20democracy%20and%20diversity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESacrifice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20pay%20my%20respects%20to%20everyone%20who%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%20for%20freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said%20at%20the%20beginning%2C%20taking%20the%20names%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Bhagat%20Singh%2C%20Sukhdev%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20that%20time%2C%20there%20was%20probably%20no%20one%20who%20did%20not%20contribute%20to%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%20The%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20which%20is%20the%20precursor%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20say%20historians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20speech%20too%2C%20Modi%20said%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20Hindustani%20who%20did%20not%20live%20with%20the%20dream%20of%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20mentioned%20Manipur%2C%20where%20ethnic%20violence%20has%20led%20to%20at%20least%20150%20deaths%20and%20very%20deep%20divisions%20among%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20communities.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20silence%20on%20the%20issue%20has%20been%20summarily%20criticised%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHatred%20was%20seen%20in%20Manipur.%20People%20had%20to%20lose%20lives.%20Games%20were%20played%20with%20mothers%E2%80%99%20and%20sisters%E2%80%99%20dignity%20but%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days%20there%20has%20been%20news%20of%20continuous%20peace.%20The%20country%20is%20with%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20people.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20people%20have%20been%20keeping%20the%20peace%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20let%20them%20continue%20it.%20Peace%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20solution.%20The%20state%20and%20Union%20government%20together%20are%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20solve%20the%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20made%20several%20mentions%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enari%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eshakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(women%20power)%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CMa%20Bharti%20(mother%20India)%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnarendra-modi-nari-shakti-independence-da