%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-indicted-georgia-trump-rico-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Giuliani%20went%20from%20RICO%20charge%20prosecutor%20to%20a%20defendant%20in%20Fulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis'%20RICO%20case%20over%20Trump's%20alleged%202020%20election%20interference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ssheth%40businessinsider.com%20(Sonam%20Sheth)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A454%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-indicted-georgia-trump-rico-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Constitution%20and%20the%20Wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15084102%2Findia-3639503_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20now%20looks%20all%20but%20certain%20that%20the%20road%20to%202024%20and%20perhaps%20beyond%20is%20going%20to%20be%20paved%20by%20the%20wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People.%20Far%20from%20being%20unidirectional%2C%20this%20anger%20is%20pluralistic%20and%20polysemic%2C%20filtering%20through%20the%20socio-economic%20fabric%20with%20devastating%20consequences%20for%20everyone%20involved%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20tragically%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20those%20who%20have%20to%20live%20with%20this%20memory%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%20For%20a%20republic%2C%20this%20rage%20is%20also%20profoundly%20consequential%20because%20it%20forces%20one%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20nature%20of%20our%20political%20arrangement%2C%20initiate%20a%20rethinking%20of%20accountability%20of%20political%20institutions%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20question%20the%20meanings%20of%20moral%20and%20political%20ideals.%20(For%20some%20examples%20of%20writings%20along%20these%20lines%20in%20light%20of%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3A%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-writes-after-manipur-our-self-serving-morality-8853454%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdouble-engine-the-union-and-state-government-must-answer-for-manipur%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanipur-violence-churachandpur-meitei-kuki-institutionalised-violence%23read-more%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20anger%20also%20brings%20to%20light%20a%20peculiar%20problem%20for%20a%20modern%20constitutional%20democracy.%20What%20happens%20when%20one%20of%20the%20cornerstone%20ideas%20of%20modern%20constitutionalism%20best%20represented%20by%20the%20preambular%20words%20%E2%80%93%20we%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20is%20invoked%20not%20in%20the%20service%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20aspiration%20but%20rather%20as%20a%20vehicle%20for%20a%20people%20who%20are%20wrathful%3F%20Can%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20resist%20a%20sustained%20assault%20from%20forces%20representing%20exclusionary%20visions%20when%20they%20claim%20to%20pursue%20such%20action%20not%20just%20from%20a%20political%20standpoint%20but%2C%20crucially%2C%20from%20a%20constitutional%20standpoint%20of%20speaking%20for%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%3F%20In%20short%2C%20how%20do%20we%20think%20about%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20as%20a%20panacea%20when%20its%20very%20preamble%20is%20used%20to%20undermine%20its%20foundational%20premise%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20collective%20destiny%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20difficult%20questions%20to%20answer%2C%20partly%20because%20constitutionalism%20in%20India%2C%20as%20elsewhere%2C%20has%20always%20been%20as%20much%20a%20political%20project%20as%20it%20has%20been%20a%20normative%20one.%20But%2C%20in%20emphasis%20and%20understanding%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20excessive%20focus%20on%20the%20normative%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20political.%20This%20presents%20at%20least%20two%20problems%20that%20are%20relevant%20to%20the%20contemporary%20crisis.%20Firstly%2C%20this%20belief%20in%20the%20promise%20and%20the%20liberal%20values%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98founding%20document%E2%80%99%20is%20invoked%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20aspirational%20relief%20when%20politics%20fails%20to%20do%20so.%20It%20is%20this%20undying%20faith%20that%20inspired%20people%20to%20come%20out%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20collectively%20read%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20constitution%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20But%2C%20in%20just%20vernacularising%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20raw%20political%20power%20embedded%20in%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20letter%20and%20spirit%20did%20not%20disappear.%20It%20was%20made%20clear%20when%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20the%20state%20stepped%20in%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20these%20protests.%20As%20a%20rights-bearing%20individual%2C%20one%20could%20always%20seek%20remedy%20from%20the%20constitution%2C%20but%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%20has%20the%20state%20given%20up%20its%20all-encompassing%20power.%20If%20anything%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20among%20the%20105%20constitutional%20amendments%20that%20have%20been%20passed%20thus%20far%2C%20with%20a%20rare%20exception%20or%20two%2C%20they%20do%20not%20grant%20or%20extend%20rights%20to%20individuals.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20several%20have%20curtailed%20the%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Indian%20Women%20Fared%20Since%20PM%20Modi%20Invoked%20Nari%20Shakti%20in%20His%20Last%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnarendra-modi-nari-shakti-independence-day%5C%22%3EHow%20Indian%20Women%20Fared%20Since%20PM%20Modi%20Invoked%20Nari%20Shakti%20in%20His%20Last%20Independence%20Day%20Speech%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20project%20of%20resuscitating%20the%20normative%20ideals%20of%20the%20constitution%20fails%20to%20appropriately%20account%20for%20people%E2%80%99s%20anger.%20In%20just%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20glimpses%20(and%20we%20know%20that%20the%20lived%20experience%20and%20reality%20of%20the%20horrific%20events%20in%20Manipur%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3EHaryana%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20places%20in%20the%20country%20are%20far%20worse)%20of%20the%20actions%20and%20consequences%20motivated%20by%20sheer%20contempt%2C%20disregard%20and%20the%20unleashing%20of%20the%20wrath%20of%20citizens%20on%20one%20another.%20It%20is%20all%20the%20more%20terrifying%20that%20minorities%20are%20being%20singularly%20and%20systematically%20targeted%20in%20an%20open%2C%20brazen%20manner%20that%20defies%20all%20moral%20norms%20for%20individuals%20and%20the%20community.%20In%20these%20times%2C%20it%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20return%20to%20the%20presumed%20idealism%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Instead%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20if%20constitutionalism%20can%20speak%20to%20the%20visceral%20anger%20of%20the%20survivors%20of%20assaults%20and%20of%20those%20who%20will%20forever%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%20And%2C%20then%2C%20one%20also%20has%20to%20think%20about%20how%20to%20account%20for%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20motivated%20by%20exclusionary%20ideologies%20and%20enabled%20by%20a%20complacent%20state%20that%20often%20looks%20the%20other%20way%20at%20the%20time%20that%20violence%20is%20committed.%20Normative%20resuscitation%20can%20only%20revive%20the%20mythical%20spirit%20of%20the%20constitution.%20It%20cannot%20revive%20the%20body%20weighed%20down%20in%20a%20state%20of%20obedience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20moves%20away%20from%20a%20strictly%20normative%20view%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20one%20finds%20a%20rich%20body%20of%20work%20that%20has%20highlighted%20several%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20constitution%20has%20been%20used%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20not%20used%20appropriately.%20But%20an%20enduring%20theme%20of%20such%20studies%20has%20been%20that%20they%20ultimately%20place%20faith%20in%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20panacea%20for%20socio-political%20ills.%20Undergirding%20the%20document%E2%80%99s%20popular%20roots%2C%20or%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20reflect%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%20as%20much%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20govern%20them%2C%20and%20arguing%20that%20the%20courts%20could%20in%20the%20ultimate%20regard%20serve%20as%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20republic%20even%20as%20all%20other%20established%20political%20institutions%20and%20mechanisms%20fail%2C%20while%20helpful%20in%20limited%20ways%2C%20nevertheless%20only%20serves%20to%20place%20the%20constitution%20on%20a%20pedestal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20one%20values%20these%20approaches%20for%20their%20obvious%20democratising%2C%20ameliorating%20and%20progressive%20impulses%20in%20limited%20ways%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20they%20fail%20to%20see%20the%20rising%20danger%20of%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20constitution%20from%20within%20rather%20than%20without.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20preambular%20invocation%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%20could%20in%20its%20own%20way%20become%20the%20ultimate%20instrument%20through%20which%20the%20edifice%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20limited%20emancipatory%20potential%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20undone.%20Saving%20the%20constitution%20from%20a%20wrathful%20people%2C%20then%2C%20becomes%20an%20urgent%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20rescue%20the%20constitution%2C%20ironically%2C%20is%20to%20lessen%20moral%20expectations%20from%20the%20document.%20There%20is%20a%20compelling%20need%20to%20do%20so%2C%20for%20otherwise%2C%20one%20is%20constantly%20forced%20to%20reinvigorate%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20document%2C%20which%20for%20the%20most%20part%20do%20not%20exist%20in%20historical%20archives%20but%20rather%20in%20carefully%20constructed%20inductive%20and%20deductive%20reasoning%20by%20scholars%20and%20likeminded%20public%20thinkers.%20%C2%A0The%20constitution%20carries%20an%20undue%20moral%20burden%20to%20speak%20to%20situations%20that%20have%20already%20far%20exceeded%20the%20context%20in%20which%20the%20document%20was%20written.%20In%20a%20proverbial%20sense%2C%20then%2C%20the%20emperor%20may%20not%20be%20naked%20but%20is%20not%20fully%20clothed%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20not%20a%20call%20for%20nihilism%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20constitution.%20Neither%20is%20it%20an%20argument%20for%20undoing%20the%20limited%20goods%20that%20a%20constitution%20does%20provide%20and%20has%20provided%20for%20millions%20since%20independence.%20Rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20call%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20constitution%20by%20remembering%20two%20precepts%3A%20First%2C%20recognise%20that%20a%20self-sustaining%20normative%20value%20of%20the%20constitution%20does%20not%20exist.%20It%20is%20a%20chimera.%20The%20Indian%20constitution%20was%20and%20has%20always%20been%20about%20protection%20and%20sharing%20of%20state%20power%2C%20not%20a%20noble%20document%20that%20exists%20to%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20citizens.%20It%20would%20be%20better%20to%20consider%20the%20constitution%20as%20a%20political%20and%20not%20a%20normative%20document.%20Several%20scholars%20have%20already%20made%20this%20important%20shift%20in%20their%20research%20on%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20Second%2C%20there%20are%20important%20lessons%20in%20Indian%20constitutional%20history%20that%20can%20provide%20a%20tentative%20pathway%20to%20effectively%20rethink%20the%20role%20that%20the%20constitution%20can%20play%20in%20the%20socio-political%20imaginaries.%20Politics%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20here%20too.%20It%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20briefly%20expand%20on%20this%20latter%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20striking%20features%20of%20constitutional%20developments%20in%20the%20early%20to%20mid-20th%20century%20is%20the%20well-known%20colonial%20context.%20Strangely%2C%20though%20written%20about%2C%20it%20is%20relatively%20under-appreciated%20in%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20emergence%20of%20constitutionalism%20in%20India.%20A%20defining%20trait%20of%20this%20context%20was%20that%20even%20as%20Britain%20wrote%20constitutional%20legislation%20for%20India%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20ultimately%20defending%20the%20project%20of%20colonialism%2C%20in%20its%20impact%20and%20implementation%20it%20offered%20ways%20to%20Indian%20nationalist%20leaders%20to%20claim%20part-ownership%20of%20governance%20and%20aspire%20for%20imagining%20complete%20autonomy.%20This%20meant%20that%20despite%20their%20best%20efforts%20to%20uniformly%20translate%20the%20political%20project%20of%20colonialism%20into%20a%20constitutional%20language%2C%20the%20endeavour%20did%20not%20succeed%20entirely.%20Likewise%2C%20for%20the%20anticolonial%20nationalists%2C%20the%20language%20of%20constitutionalism%20forced%20the%20language%20of%20representation%2C%20which%20offered%20an%20opportunity%20for%20different%20regional%20and%20national%20interests%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20own%20voices.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20process%20never%20allowed%20for%20a%20way%20to%20translate%20the%20mythical%20idea%20of%20national%20unity%20into%20a%20constitutional%20project.%20Constitutionalism%2C%20by%20its%20very%20nature%20and%20because%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20competing%20political%20interests%2C%20prevented%20the%20hegemony%20of%20a%20single%20representative%20group.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20for%20leaders%20of%20both%20colonialism%20and%20nationalism%2C%20constitutionalism%20never%20emerged%20as%20a%20faithful%20ally%20for%20their%20respective%20political%20projects.%20The%20relationship%20between%20them%20was%20always%20tension-prone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi's%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20precisely%20the%20productivity%20of%20this%20tension%20that%20helped%20different%20interested%20groups%20to%20stake%20a%20claim%20in%20the%20making%20of%20the%20constitution.%20For%20instance%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20rigorous%20defence%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20Dalits%20and%20M.A.%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20stance%20on%20Pakistan%20had%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20constitutional%20space%20that%20opened%20up%20in%20the%20colonial%20context.%20Likewise%2C%20others%20such%20as%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20princely%20states%20similarly%20put%20forward%20their%20constitutional%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20there%20is%20an%20important%20lesson%20to%20be%20learnt%20from%20this%20highly%20abbreviated%20account%20of%20Indian%20constitutional%20history%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20the%20story%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20one%20of%20securing%20state%20power%2C%20and%20the%20colonial%20context%20enabled%20the%20proliferation%20of%20different%20political%20interests%2C%20each%20making%20their%20own%20claims%20on%20such%20power.%20In%20the%20postcolonial%20context%2C%20with%20the%20establishment%20and%20entrenchment%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20opportunity%20provided%20by%20the%20colonial%20context%20disappeared%2C%20leading%20the%20different%20politically%20organised%20groups%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20language%20of%20nationalism%20or%20risk%20being%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20then%2C%20constitutionalism%20is%20often%20strongest%20when%20there%20are%20multiple%20competing%20political%20interests.%20It%20is%20compromised%20when%20there%20is%20a%20singular%2C%20strong%20political%20force%20dominant%20in%20the%20country.%20If%20constitutionalism%20is%20to%20regain%20its%20strength%2C%20then%20the%20solution%20may%20not%20be%20to%20look%20to%20the%20constitution%20from%20an%20apolitical%20or%20normative%20point%20of%20view%20but%20rather%20to%20understand%20and%20engage%20with%20its%20fundamentally%20political%20character.%20This%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20not%20only%20save%20the%20people%20from%20the%20constitution%20but%20importantly%2C%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20constitution%20from%20the%20wrath%20of%20(We)%20the%20People.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArvind%20Elangovan%20is%20Professor%20of%20History%20and%20Associate%20Chair%2C%20School%20of%20Humanities%20and%20Cultural%20Studies%2C%20College%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%2C%20Wright%20State%20University%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692069121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15084102%2Findia-3639503_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20preambular%20invocation%20of%20%E2%80%98we%20the%20people%E2%80%99%20could%20in%20its%20own%20way%20become%20the%20ultimate%20instrument%20through%20which%20the%20edifice%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20limited%20emancipatory%20potential%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20undone.%20Saving%20the%20constitution%20from%20a%20wrathful%20people%2C%20then%2C%20becomes%20an%20urgent%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-constitution-and-the-wrath-of-we-the-people%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Indicted%20in%20Georgia%20on%202020%20Election%20Interference%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692068777000%2C%22v