0new%20lease%20of%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MINI%20THOMAS%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fdrug-coated-balloon-gives-new-life-to-man-who-had-over-100-strokes%2Farticleshow%2F102737413.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi's%20India%3A%20Empowering%20the%20Mob%2C%20Disempowering%20the%20State%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Manipur%20to%20Mewat%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20new%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20portray%20a%20pretty%20picture.%20It%20is%20a%20holy%20mess.%20The%20shift%20in%20nomenclature%20from%20Amrit%20Kaal%20(auspicious%20period)%20to%20Kartavya%20Kaal%20(period%20of%20duty)%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20a%20complete%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20political%20leadership.%20It%20has%20hampered%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20which%20have%20consequently%20failed%20to%20bring%20the%20violence%20under%20control.%20But%20this%20is%20no%20ordinary%20violence%20of%20a%20communal%20riot%20or%20a%20socio-economic%20protest%20that%20independent%20India%20has%20been%20witness%20to%20many%20a%20time%20in%20the%20first%20seven%20decades%20of%20its%20existence.%20It%20is%20not%20even%20an%20insurgency%20like%20Kashmir%20or%20Punjab%20or%20Nagaland%20or%20Mizoram.%20The%20violence%20is%20not%20due%20to%20criminal%20gangs%20shooting%20each%20other%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai.%20These%20are%20not%20misguided%20youth%20taking%20up%20guns%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20communist%20revolution.%20This%20is%20different%3A%20violence%20with%20a%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20mobs.%20Mobs%2C%20who%20have%20been%20empowered%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20political%20leadership%20is%20not%20simply%20condoning%20their%20action%20or%20looking%20away%3B%20it%20is%20using%20these%20mobs%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20State%20against%20a%20minority%20community.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20majoritarian%20Meitei%20mobs%20are%20enabled%20by%20allowing%20ransacking%20of%20lethal%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20police%20armouries.%20The%20proof%20lies%20in%20the%20bewildering%20fact%20that%20not%20a%20single%20miscreant%20was%20caught%20or%20shot%20by%20the%20cops%20as%20these%20armouries%20were%20supposedly%20being%20looted.%20Call%20it%20connivance%20or%20collusion%20or%20co-option%2C%20or%20all%20of%20the%20above%2C%20the%20mobs%20are%20the%20masters%20of%20this%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20control%20them%3B%20they%20control%20the%20state%20and%20are%20aware%20of%20their%20power.%20Invariably%2C%20these%20mobs%20belong%20to%20the%20majority%20community%20and%20are%20politically%20from%20the%20same%20parivar%20as%20the%20party%20ruling%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre.%20It%20is%20the%20reason%20they%20are%20empowered%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Their%20public%20acceptance%20as%20custodians%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20popular%20culture%20and%20public%20morality%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20mandate%2C%20except%20their%20brute%20power%20to%20inflict%20violence.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20incorrect%20to%20see%20them%20as%20adherents%20of%20VD%20Savarkar%E2%80%99s%20dictum%2C%20as%20cited%20by%20Prof%20Vinayak%20Chaturvedi%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20understand%20themselves%20as%20Hindus%20through%20acts%20of%20violence%E2%80%9D.%20The%20danger%20lies%20in%20these%20mobs%20trying%20to%20ensure%20what%20Savarkar%20desired%20of%20Hindus%3A%20they%20%E2%80%9Cneeded%20to%20embrace%20permanent%20war%20as%20part%20of%20their%20future%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20RPF%20cop%20Chetan%20Singh%20identifies%2C%20selects%20and%20kills%20Muslims%2C%20that%20future%20seems%20to%20be%20upon%20us%20now.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20lone%20wolf%20but%20the%20representative%20of%20an%20empowered%20mob.%20The%20lines%20between%20the%20mob%20and%20cops%20have%20blurred.%20In%20both%20Manipur%20and%20Mewat%2C%20this%20mob%20is%20indistinguishable%20from%20the%20cops.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20reports%20show%20the%20two%20working%20in%20tandem%2C%20jointly%20targeting%20the%20minority%20community.%20In%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20poor%2C%20marginalised%2C%20and%20subordinated%20sometimes%20resort%20to%20violence%2C%20often%20genocidal%20in%20nature%20%E2%80%93%20at%20times%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20state%2C%20in%20other%20instances%20independent%20of%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20order%20to%20stake%20a%20claim%20within%E2%80%A6to%20make%20history%20as%20killers%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Hindutva%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmpowering%20the%20violent%20and%20hateful%20mob%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20strengthen%20the%20Indian%20State.%20It%20weakens%20and%20hollows%20it%20out.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20state%20has%20simply%20ceased%20to%20exist.%20In%20Mewat%2C%20the%20state%20has%20no%20credibility%20left.%20Few%20trust%20it%20anymore%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20epithet%20BJP%20used%20to%20unleash%20on%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20It%20is%20a%20disempowered%20state%2C%20where%20the%20mob%20has%20been%20empowered%20at%20its%20cost.%20This%20disempowerment%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20remain%20limited%20to%20one%20aspect%20or%20geography.%20Slowly%20but%20surely%2C%20it%20encroaches%20on%20to%20other%20domains%20and%20areas%2C%20sapping%20the%20state%20of%20its%20energies%20to%20accomplish%20even%20the%20minimum%20obligatory%20tasks.%20We%20need%20look%20no%20further%20than%20Pakistan%20to%20see%20where%20this%20path%20leads%20to.%20It%20is%20surprising%20that%20those%20who%20imagine%20India%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Pakistan%E2%80%9D%20can%20be%20so%20blind%20to%20the%20eventual%20destination%20of%20their%20desired%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20disempowered%20state%2C%20flailing%20and%20fouling%2C%20is%20doomed%20for%20disaster.%20Vigilantism%20is%20one%20of%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20this%20journey.%20We%20have%20witnessed%20it%20enough%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cow%20protection%20or%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99.%20In%20no%20other%20modern%20civilised%20society%20have%20so%20many%20men%20been%20publicly%20lynched%20as%20have%20been%20in%20India%20by%20Hindutva%20vigilante%20groups.%20The%20vigilantism%20of%20the%20cops%20is%20well%20known%2C%20but%20that%20crossed%20a%20limit%20in%20Gujarat%20when%20the%20state%20police%20publicly%20flogged%20young%20Muslims%20and%20made%20a%20video%20of%20it.%20Even%20the%20Taliban%20regime%20in%20Afghanistan%20claimed%20a%20moral%20high%20ground%20over%20Gujarat%20Police%20after%20that%20video!%20Gujarat%20has%20seen%20unbroken%20BJP%20rule%20this%20century%2C%20and%20makes%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20top%20political%2C%20bureaucratic%20and%20business%20leadership%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%20It%20was%20sold%20as%20the%20model%20state%20in%202014%2C%20which%20many%20gullible%20Indians%20fell%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20gaze%20into%20the%20abyss%2C%20the%20abyss%20gazes%20also%20into%20you.%E2%80%9D%20Nietzsche%20may%20have%20meant%20it%20differently%20but%20when%20a%20state%20gazes%20adoringly%20into%20the%20abyss%20of%20a%20mob%2C%20it%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20becoming%20the%20mob.%20The%20use%20of%20bulldozers%20to%20target%20residential%20and%20commercial%20properties%20of%20Muslims%2C%20ostensibly%20for%20violation%20of%20municipal%20rules%2C%20is%20vigilantism%20by%20the%20state.%20It%20breeds%20misery%20and%20hate.%20It%20destroys%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20sounds%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20our%20constitutional%20order.%20The%20state%20has%20turned%20into%20an%20unjust%20monster%2C%20trying%20to%20impose%20a%20new%20moral%20order%20%E2%80%93%20an%20immoral%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mutation%20had%20no%20place%20in%20the%20India%20that%20was%20imagined%20in%20the%20crucible%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20shaped%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20The%20bulldozer%20is%20the%20symbol%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20new%20India.%20It%20is%20the%20icon%20of%20vigilantism%20and%20mob%20empowerment.%20It%20is%20the%20withering%20away%20of%20the%20tate%20through%20deliberate%20disempowerment.%20A%20disempowered%20state%20can%20be%20the%20stepfather%20of%20despotism%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy.%20It%20can%20be%20majoritarian%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20democratic.%20It%20can%20be%20new%20India%2C%20but%20it%20will%20not%20be%20our%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fempowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state-2645701%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2F%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692066602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20no%20other%20modern%20civilised%20society%20have%20so%20many%20men%20been%20publicly%20lynched%20as%20have%20been%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodis-india-empowering-the-mob-disempowering-the-state%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20office%20records%20broken%20by%20Gadar%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692066600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102733272%2Cimgsize-18494.cms%22