e%20nation%20and%20Twitter%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape%20erupted%20in%20rage%20at%20a%20video%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20naked%20parading%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%20amidst%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20has%20seen%20women%20being%20raped%2C%20their%20bodies%20brutalised%20with%20reports%20noted%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20%E2%80%9Chanded%20over%E2%80%9D%20to%20armed%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%202023%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20of%20Manipur%20has%20put%20140%20crore%20Indians%20to%20shame%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20daughters%20of%20Manipur%20can%20never%20be%20forgiven%2C%20the%20guilty%20will%20not%20be%20spared%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20video.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20operative%20word%20here%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshame%E2%80%9D.%20The%20other%20operative%20word%20here%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdaughters%E2%80%9D.%20Just%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20evoked%20the%20collective%20shame%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians%2C%20many%20expressed%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etheir%20own%20masculine%20shame%20at%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdaughters%2C%20mothers%2C%20and%20sisters%E2%80%9D.%20This%20underlined%2C%20once%20again%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20women%20after%20all%20belong%20to%20men%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20don%E2%80%99t%20belong%20to%20themselves%3B%20their%20bodies%20are%20sites%20where%20symbols%20of%20masculinity%20are%20often%20stamped%20in%20acts%20of%20hate%2C%20rage%2C%20vengeance%20and%20violence%2C%20with%20men%20of%20opposing%20clans%20teaching%20a%20lesson%20to%20each%20other%20by%20punishing%20their%20women.%20This%20has%20been%20an%20age-old%20custom%2C%20prevalent%20from%20the%20times%20of%20wars%20over%20fiefdoms%20and%20among%20land-owning%20feudal%20classes.%20This%20mediaeval%20mindset%20has%20undergone%20several%20rites%20of%20passage%2C%20earning%20a%20modern%20currency%20of%20relevance%20and%20prestige%20during%20the%20Indian%20nationalist%20movement%20with%20Bharat%20Mata%20becoming%20the%20leitmotif%20of%20the%20nation%20itself.%20Later%20in%20independent%20India%2C%20women%20have%20often%20borne%20the%20burden%20of%20nationalism%20through%20social%20roles%2C%20codes%20of%20dressing%20and%20moral%20duties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20conversation%20never%20about%20the%20women%20and%20the%20violence%20against%20their%20bodily%20autonomy%2C%20the%20assault%20on%20their%20identity%2C%20their%20dignity%20and%20their%20health%3F%20Why%20is%20it%20that%20only%20when%20Indian%20men%20feel%20ashamed%20or%20outraged%20that%20the%20nation%20must%20rise%20from%20its%20apolitical%20slumber%3F%C2%A0%20Who%20decides%20who%20deserves%20justice%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWrestlers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20same%20year%2C%20Olympic%20and%20Worlds%20medal-winning%20women%20wrestlers%20protesting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20were%20forcibly%20removed%20and%20allegedly%20attacked%20by%20police.%20They%20were%20protesting%20against%20police%20inaction%20against%20outgoing%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20and%20BJP%20MP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprofile-on-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh%2Farticle66928654.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20the%20female%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20wrestlers%20including%20heavyweights%20like%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20who%20are%20otherwise%20hailed%20as%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20ki%20Beti%E2%80%9D%20upon%20winning%20medals%20and%20bringing%20laurels%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20were%20accused%20of%20having%20political%20agenda%20in%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20workplace%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20a%20raging%20issue%20of%20our%20time%2C%20was%20trivialised%20and%20the%20powerful%20wrestlers%20were%20rendered%20defenceless%20against%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20predator%2C%20the%2066-year-old%20Singh.%20Malik%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20seven%20days%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20sexual%20harasser%20Brij%20Bhushan%2C%20and%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20take%20seven%20hours%20to%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20us%20for%20peacefully%20protesting%20%5Bduring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tweeted.%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20country%20under%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edictatorship%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20The%20whole%20world%20is%20watching%20how%20the%20government%20is%20treating%20its%20players.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20remarked%20that%20this%20is%20indeed%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F5%2F28%2Fworld-is-watching-indian-police-drag-away-protesting-wrestlers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eculture%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20WFI.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20head%20himself%20is%20like%20that%2C%20what%20action%20will%20he%20take%20against%20others%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20on%20August%2011%2C%202023%2C%20Delhi%20police%20said%20that%20there%20is%20enough%20evidence%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprofile-on-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh%2Farticle66928654.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20him%20to%20be%20put%20on%20trial%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdelhi-court-brij-bhushan%2Farticle67107090.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esexual%20harassment%20case%20filed%20by%20women%20wrestlers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20had%20filed%20a%201%2C000-page%20chargesheet%20on%20June%2015%20against%20the%20accused%20for%20offences%20under%20Sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20and%20354D%20(stalking)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20Police%20have%20not%20opposed%20his%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EC.K.%20Raulji%2C%20the%20sitting%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MLA%20from%20Godhra%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbilkis-banos-rapists-are-brahmins-have-good-sanskar-bjp-mla-3266193%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EBrahmins%2C%20and%20Brahmins%20are%20known%20to%20have%20good%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esanskaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(culture).%20It%20might%20have%20been%20someone%E2%80%99s%20ill%20intention%20to%20corner%20and%20punish%20them.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20of%20the%2011%20rape%20convicts%20set%20free%20in%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Findia%2Fbilkis-bano-rape-case-vhp-greets-released-convicts-with-garlands-in-gujarat-article-93620902%5C%22%3Egreeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20released%20rape%20convicts%20with%20garlands%20at%20its%20office%20in%20Gujarat.%20Visuals%20showed%20relatives%20including%20women%20greeting%20the%20rape%20convicts%20with%20sweets%20and%20%3Ci%3Echaran-sparsh%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3Etouching%20their%20feet%20for%20blessings%2C%20outside%20the%20Godhra%20jail.%20Many%20might%20call%20it%20bizarre%2C%20but%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20it%20was%20a%20deliberately%20mounted%20optics%2C%20the%20message%20was%20loud%20and%20clear%3A%20You%20would%20be%20rewarded%20for%20perpetrating%20hate%20crimes%20and%20raping%20or%20gang-raping%20women%2C%20especially%20minority%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-video-kuki-women-stripped-manorama-bilkis-bano%5C%22%3EManipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EHijab%20ban%2C%20denying%20a%20generation%20of%20girls%20their%20right%20to%20education%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20upheld%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20state%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20suggested%20that%20government%20colleges%20with%20uniform%20codes%20are%20well%20within%20their%20rights%20to%20put%20a%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20restriction%E2%80%9D%20on%20Muslim%20female%20students%20wearing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijabs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20Muslim%20girls%20were%20barred%20from%20taking%20examinations%20and%20several%20found%20their%20bodily%20autonomy%20threatened%20and%20violated%20as%20invigilators%20and%20institutional%20gatekeepers%20instructed%20them%20to%20take%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20off%20before%20entering%20the%20educational%20premises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20stated%20that%20the%20total%20dropouts%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E-wearing%20girls%20stand%20at%201%2C010%20because%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ban%20(or%20other%20reasons%20as%20well)%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fhijab-ban-one-year-on-muslim-students-in-karnataka-continue-their-fight-for-education-news-267990%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPUCL%20fact-finding%20report%20released%20in%20September%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20the%20Modi-led%20NDA%20alliance%2C%20which%20has%20prided%20itself%20on%20its%20noble%20mission%20of%20liberating%20Muslim%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esisters%20and%20daughters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20tyranny%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhijab-ban-narendra-modi-muslim-women-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20triple%20talaq%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20would%20deny%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20education%2C%20the%20biggest%20gateway%20to%20progress%2C%20discriminating%20them%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20what%20they%20choose%20to%20wear.%20The%20debate%20in%20this%20context%20amid%20a%20culture%20of%20persecuting%20a%20community%20is%20not%20about%20whether%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20liberating%20or%20not%2C%20but%20the%20choice%20to%20wear%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehijab%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20not%20should%20solely%20lie%20with%20Muslim%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20time%20to%20clearly%20spell%20it%20out%20that%20fascism%20and%20hate%20can%20never%20be%20the%20foundation%20of%20feminism%20or%20any%20effort%20that%20seeks%20to%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20of%20women.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERemember%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20octogenarian%20grandmother%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Ffeatures%2F2021%2F3%2F8%2Fbilkis-dadi-of-shaheen-bagh-a-modern-day-rani-ki-jhansi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBilkis%20Dadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EShaheen%20Bagh%20protesting%20against%20the%20discriminatory%20%3C%2Fs