0month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1948574%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2014%2C%20showed%20that%20retail%20inflation%20easily%20breached%20the%20upper%20limit%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20tolerance%20band%20of%202%25%20to%206%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20(CPI)%20inflation%20for%20July%20is%20a%20huge%20jump%20of%20257%20basis%20points%20compared%20to%20the%20revised%20June%20number%20of%204.87%25.%20It%20is%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20it%20is%20the%2046th%20month%20in%20a%20row%20that%20it%20has%20surpassed%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20medium-term%20target%20of%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20a%20poll%20of%2053%20economists%20who%20had%20estimated%20that%20the%20CPI%20inflation%20would%20rise%20up%20to%206.40%25%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%20on%20rising%20food%20prices.%20However%2C%20the%20latest%20figure%20show%20that%20it%20has%20even%20exceeded%20the%20expectation%20of%20economists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Findia-july-retail-inflation-cpi-data-consumer-price-index-8892350%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%204.49%25%20in%20June%2C%20the%20consumer%20food%20price%20index%20(CFPI)%20jumped%20to%2011.51%25.%20And%2C%20the%20rural%20inflation%20rate%20in%20July%20rose%20to%207.63%25%20year-on-year%20from%204.78%25%20in%20July.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20urban%20inflation%20witnessed%20a%20jump%20from%204.96%25%20to%207.20%25%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20RBI%20keeping%20policy%20rates%20unchanged%20at%206.50%25%20in%20its%20August%20monetary%20policy%20review.%20However%2C%20it%20raised%20the%20forecast%20for%20CPI%20inflation%20for%20fiscal%202024%20from%205.1%25%20to%205.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20has%20already%20predicted%20that%20the%20inflation%20rate%20would%20see%20a%20further%20rise%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20owing%20to%20skyrocketing%20vegetable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hoping%20that%20the%20surging%20vegetable%20prices%20may%20soon%20see%20a%20downward%20trend%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Findia-july-retail-inflation-cpi-data-consumer-price-index-8892350%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cpossible%20El%20Nino%20weather%20conditions%2C%20along%20with%20global%20food%20prices%20need%20to%20be%20watched%20closely%2C%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20skewed%20Southwest%20Monsoon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692034540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F08200712%2FScreen-Shot-2020-04-08-at-8.06.53-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fat-15-month-high-retail-inflation-in-july-jumped-to-7-44-owing-to-soaring-vegetable-prices%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20data%20released%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20showed%20that%20retail%20inflation%20breached%20the%20upper%20limit%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20tolerance%20band%20of%202%25-6%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20five%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fat-15-month-high-retail-inflation-in-july-jumped-to-7-44-owing-to-soaring-vegetable-prices%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20estimates%3A%20ITC's%20profit%20puffs%20up%20over%2016%25%20to%20Rs%205%2C104.%2093%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692033681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsme