08.%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20the%20fines%20that%20you%20impose%3F%20How%20much%20does%20the%20TV%20channel%20make%20from%20an%20advertisement%20in%20one%20program%3F%20No%20TV%20channel%20has%20any%20motivation%20to%20comply%20with%20your%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%2C%20and%20if%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20violation%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20impose%20a%20penalty%20of%20a%20lakh%20of%20rupees%2C%20there%20you%20have%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20penalties%20imposed%20on%20TV%20channels%20for%20airing%20disputed%20news%20must%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20profits%20earned%2C%20rather%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20fine%2C%20fixed%20way%20back%20in%202008.%20Only%20such%20fines%20can%20act%20as%20a%20deterrent%20for%20television%20channels%20to%20act%20with%20responsibility%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20CJI%2C%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20NBDA%20challenging%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%202021%20verdict%20that%20contained%20adverse%20observations%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20teeth%20in%20the%20self-regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20held%20that%20trial%20by%20media%20interferes%20with%20the%20criminal%20investigation%20by%20police%20and%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%20to%20the%20media%20to%20be%20followed%20while%20reporting%20incidents%20involving%20suicide%20and%20death%20of%20persons.%20The%20high%20court%20was%20back%20then%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20questioning%20the%20media%20trial%20in%20the%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%E2%80%99s%20death%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20agreeing%20with%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20no%20government%20interference%20in%20regulating%20the%20media%2C%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%20has%20to%20be%20effective.%20The%20CJI%20said%20it%20will%20issue%20guidelines%20to%20strengthen%20the%20regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692032395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpenalties-on-tv-channels-for-airing-disputed-news-must-be-proportionate-to-profits-says-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20observing%20that%20the%20current%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%20by%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20in%20force%20is%20not%20effective%2C%20vowing%20to%20issue%20guidelines%20to%20strengthen%20the%20regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpenalties-on-tv-channels-for-airing-disputed-news-must-be-proportionate-to-profits-says-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22N%20Ireland%20police%20details%20in%20hands%20of%20dissident%20republicans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692031794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F49FA%2Fproduction%2F_130783981_policehaveclosedtheroadinportadown02.jpgpacemaker.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-northern-ireland-66479818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chief%20constable%20says%20the%20information%20could%20be%20used%20to%20intimidate%20or%20target%20officers%20and%20staff.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A213%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-northern-ireland-66479818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-northern-ireland-66479818.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-northern-ireland-66479818.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22