2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Fgoa-becomes-first-state-to-provide-ivf-free-at-govt-hospital%2Farticleshow%2F102730330.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Escaped%20lion%20shot%20dead%20in%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692024780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F70x70%2Fskynews-lioness-south-korea_6250741.jpg%3F20230814163059%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fescaped-lioness-shot-dead-in-south-korea-12939999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20escaped%20lioness%20has%20been%20shot%20dead%20in%20South%20Korea%20after%20an%20emergency%20search%20involving%20more%20than%20100%20police%2C%20firefighters%20and%20hunters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A146%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fescaped-lioness-shot-dead-in-south-korea-12939999%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fescaped-lioness-shot-dead-in-south-korea-12939999%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fescaped-lioness-shot-dead-in-south-korea-12939999%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Lunar%20Mission%20Mission%20Tells%20Us%20About%20Its%20Future%20Plans%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F04122047%2Fsatellite-67718_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Russia%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fspace%2Frussia-launch-lunar-spacecraft-race-find-water-moon-2023-08-10%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%20called%20Luna%2025%20on%20August%2011%2C%202023%20(Indian%20Standard%20Time)%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20discussion%20that%20it%20may%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20space%20race.%20This%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20lunar%20lander%20mission%20in%2047%20years.%20It%20could%20even%20be%20viewed%20as%20the%20first%20Russian%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%20since%20all%20the%20earlier%20missions%20were%20undertaken%20during%20the%20Soviet%20era.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Russian%20space%20agency%20Roscosmos%2C%20Luna%2025%20is%20likely%20to%20reach%20the%20moon%20in%20five%20days%20and%20remain%20in%20the%20lunar%20orbit%20for%20five%20to%20seven%20days%20before%20attempting%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20The%20agency%20has%20already%20narrowed%20down%20on%20two%20or%20three%20potential%20landing%20spots%20which%20are%20close%20to%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20These%20sites%20are%20within%20a%2015-km%20wide%20and%2030-km%20long%20area.%20If%20successful%2C%20the%20mission%20will%20last%20for%20one%20year%20and%20involve%20undertaking%20various%20observations%20and%20scientific%20experiments.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole%20is%20a%20big%20area%20and%20none%20of%20these%20landing%20zones%20are%20%E2%80%98dissecting%E2%80%99%20the%20proposed%20landing%20site%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-launch-successful%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mission%E2%80%99s%20Luna-Glob-Lander%20weighs%20around%20800%20kg%20(plus%20950%20kg%20of%20fuel)%2C%20and%20has%20four%20legs%20with%20landing%20rockets%2C%20fuel%20tanks%20and%20solar%20panels.%20It%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20study%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20south%20polar%20soil%2C%20the%20plasma%20and%20dust%20present%20in%20the%20very%20thin%20lunar%20exosphere.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20Luna%2025%E2%80%99s%20lander%20(there%20is%20no%20rover%20unit%20like%20Chandrayaan-3)%20has%20a%20robotic%20arm%2C%20which%20can%20move%20in%20different%20directions%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20scoop%20to%20collect%20lunar%20samples.%20There%20are%20various%20other%20instruments%20to%20study%20the%20samples%20and%20the%20lunar%20exosphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20robotic%20arm%20has%20a%20tool%20(4.7%20cm-long%20tube)%20and%20scooper%20to%20hold%20nearly%20175%20cubic%20cm%20of%20material.%20The%20lander%20has%20eight%20scientific%20tools%20to%20collect%20data%20and%20undertake%20experimentation.%20Broadly%2C%20assessments%20like%20measuring%20the%20gamma%20rays%20and%20neutrons%20coming%20from%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%2C%20measuring%20water%20content%20on%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20and%20studying%20the%20composition%20and%20thermal%20proteins%20of%20the%20regolith%20(lunar%20dust)%20would%20be%20undertaken.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20embarked%20on%20its%20quest%20for%20the%20moon%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan-1%20in%202008%2C%20Russia%20(as%20the%20erstwhile%20Soviet%20Union)%20is%20an%20old%20player.%20The%20Luna%20Program%E2%80%99s%20first%20mission%20was%20in%201959.%20Subsequently%2C%2024%20other%20missions%20were%20carried%20out%20until%201976%20%E2%80%93%20including%20some%20failures.%20All%20these%20missions%20had%20different%20goals%3A%20flyby%20missions%2C%20missions%20involving%20the%20craft%20orbiting%20the%20moon%20and%20some%20soft%20landings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20news%20reports%20have%20noted%20that%20though%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20mission%20was%20launched%20after%20India%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbeat%E2%80%9D%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20by%20reaching%20the%20lunar%20surface%20faster.%20It%20needs%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20had%20already%20accomplished%20many%20%E2%80%98firsts%E2%80%99%20in%20this%20domain.%20They%20were%20the%20first%20to%20undertake%20a%20flyby%20mission%20of%20the%20moon%2C%20to%20have%20a%20lunar%20satellite%20and%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20(drop%20equipment%20to%20reach%20the%20lunar%20surface)%20on%20the%20moon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20during%20the%20Chandrayaan-1%20mission%20on%20November%2014%2C%202008%2C%20India%20also%20dropped%20the%20Moon%20Impact%20Probe%20on%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20surface.%20India%20became%20the%20first%20country%20to%20do%20this%20on%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Soviets%20were%20also%20the%20first%20to%20take%20photographs%20of%20the%20far%20side%20of%20the%20moon.%20They%20also%20achieved%20the%20first%20lunar%20soft%20landing%2C%20deployed%20a%20lunar%20rover%20and%20undertook%20an%20analysis%20of%20lunar%20soil.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20also%20brought%20back%20the%20first%20lunar%20sample%20to%20the%20Earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20Luna%20Program%2C%20the%20Soviets%20also%20had%20a%20program%20called%20Zond%2C%20which%20looked%20at%20the%20moon%2C%20Mars%2C%20and%20Venus.%20This%20robotic%20spacecraft%20programme%20(1964-1970)%20had%20two%20spacecraft%20series%2C%20one%20for%20interplanetary%20exploration%2C%20and%20the%20other%20for%20lunar%20exploration.%20One%20very%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20this%20programme%20was%20that%20during%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spacecentre.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fspace-now-blog%2Fzond-5-tortoises-at-the-moon%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520mission%2520would%2520last%2520for%2Cas%2520they%2520are%2520sometimes%2520known.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EZond%205%20mission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20first%20terrestrial%20organisms%20%E2%80%93%20two%20tortoises%20and%20some%20other%20lifeforms%20%E2%80%93%20survived%20their%20journey%20around%20the%20moon%20in%20a%20capsule%20and%20returned%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20Cold%20War%20period%2C%20the%20Soviets%20and%20the%20US%20competed%20for%20superior%20space%20technology.%20The%20Soviets%20demonstrated%20their%20capability%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20send%20a%20satellite%20to%20space%20(Sputnik%2C%201957)%2C%20and%20the%20first%20human%20to%20space%20(Yuri%20Gagarin%2C%201957).%20However%2C%20they%20were%20defeated%20by%20the%20US%20in%20manned%20lunar%20missions%20(starting%20with%20Apollo%2011%20in%201969).%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20(or%20Russia)%20was%20not%20able%20to%20undertake%20a%20human%20mission%20to%20the%20moon.%20Their%20human%20lunar%20programme%20was%20kept%20secret%20and%20details%20of%20it%20were%20made%20public%20only%20in%201990.%20The%20Zond%20programme%20had%20some%20focus%20on%20developing%20a%20human%20lunar%20programme.%20In%20addition%2C%20from%201969%20to%201972%2C%20they%20undertook%20four%20tests%20(all%20unsuccessful)%20of%20the%20N1%2FL3%20rocket%2C%20a%20super%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%2C%20possibly%20the%20Soviet%20counterpart%20to%20the%20US%20Saturn%20V%2C%20which%20was%20used%20for%20the%20manner%20moon%20mission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20by%20naming%20its%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%20%E2%80%9CLuna%2025%E2%80%9D%2C%20Russia%20is%20clearly%20demonstrating%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20Soviet%20space%20legacy.%20Russia%20understands%20that%20its%20cosiness%20with%20the%20US%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20space%20%E2%80%93%20which%20began%20post-Cold%20War%20with%20collaboration%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20%E2%80%93%20has%20no%20future%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2Frussia-war-ukraine-damage-international-spaceflight-cooperation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eowing%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%202021%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%20unveiled%20their%20roadmap%20to%20send%20humans%20to%20the%20moon%20by%20building%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2Fchina-russia-international-lunar-research-station%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20Lunar%20Research%20Station%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%2021st-century%20space%20race%2C%20the%20Russians%20are%20late%20starters%20and%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20match%20the%20ambitions%20of%20the%20US%20or%20China%20in%20taking%20humans%20to%20the%20moon.%20However%2C%20Russia%20could%20try%20to%20regain%20some%20of%20its%20past%20glory%20by%20collaborating%20with%20friendly%20nations%20like%20China%20and%20Iran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAjey%20Lele%20researches%20space%20issues%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3EInstitutions%20That%20Shaped%20Modern%20India%3A%20ISRO%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692024343000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F04122047%2Fsatellite-67718_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Frussia-moon-agenda-luna-25%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luna%2025%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20lunar%20lander%20mission%20in%2047%20years.%20It%20could%20even%20be%20viewed%20as%20the%20first%20Russian%20mission%20to%20the%20moon%20since%20all%20the%20earlier%20missions%20were%20undertaken%20during%20the%20Soviet%20era.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Frussia-moon-agenda-luna-25%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Evictions%20as%20the%20Latest%20Tool%20of%20Citizenship%20Exclusion%20in%20Assam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172315%2FUntitled-design-4.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20bulldozed%20the%20home%20of%2017-year-old%20Jesmina%20Khatun.%20Along%20with%20250%20other%20families%2C%20Jesmina%20and%20her%20three%20younger%20siblings%20were%20left%20with%20no%20provision%20of%20resettlement%20or%20rehabilitation.%20Their%20late%20parents%20were%20wage%20labourers%20who%20died%20landless%2C%20leaving%20three%20orphans%20to%20work%20as%20child%20labourers%20to%20survive.%20This%20is%20the%20story%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20landless%20people%20in%20Assam%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20poorest%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eviction%20drive%20unleashed%20in%20December%20last%20year%20in%20Bhumuraguri%2C%20Lalong%20Gaon%2C%20and%20Haidubi%20of%20Nagaon%20district%20forcibly%20removed%20families%20from%20homes%20they%20had%20been%20living%20in%20for%20half%20a%20century.%20Nothing%20was%20spared.%20School%20bags%20and%20books%20of%20students%20preparing%20for%20board%20exams%20were%20thrown%20into%20ponds%20%E2%80%93%20even%20plants%20were%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2.jpg%20962w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2-300x231.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22741%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJesmina%20Khatun.%20Photo%3A%20Nazimuddin%20Siddique%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20eviction%2C%20the%20victims%20had%20no%20place%20to%20go%2C%20and%20they%20end%20up%20taking%20shelter%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20village%20roads.%20The%20administration%20also%20removed%20them%20from%20the%20village%20roads.%20They%20survived%20with%20%3Cem%3EChira-%20Muri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flattened%20rice-puffed%20rice)%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20three%20days%20without%20food.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20even%20water%20to%20drink.%20This%20author%20saw%20them%20drinking%20water%20from%20dirty%20ponds.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20long%20before%20another%20brutal%20eviction%20was%20carried%20out%20against%2047%20families%20in%20the%20Satra%20Kanra%20area%20of%20Baghbar%2C%20Barpeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20%E2%80%98criminal%E2%80%99%20eviction%20drives%20have%20been%20continuing%20in%20different%20places.%20What%20do%20these%20evictions%20all%20have%20in%20common%3F%20They%20are%20against%20Miya%20Muslims%20who%20moved%20from%20erstwhile%20Bengal.%20Instead%20of%20solving%20the%20underlying%20problems%20of%20poverty%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20using%20disproportionate%20force%20and%20targeted%20threats%20against%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fvideos%2Fmirror-now%2Fsociety%2Fmassive-eviction-drive-against-illegal-immigrants-in-assam-video-96348994%5C%22%3Eillegal%20encroachers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%20While%20the%20homes%20of%20Muslims%20are%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20landless%20people%20belonging%20to%20different%20tribes%2C%20religions%2C%20and%20linguistic%20groups%20have%20been%20living%20on%20government%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20in%20the%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%2C%20an%20autonomous%20council%20of%20Assam%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20eviction%20notices%20were%20selectively%20issued%20predominantly%20to%20Muslims%20in%20several%20areas%20of%20different%20districts.%20These%20include%20Hasraobari%2C%20Mauzabari%2C%20Donshiapara%20of%20Chirang%20district%2C%20and%20Nk%20Darranga%20of%20Tamulpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20509px)%2085vw%2C%20509px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc.jpg%20509w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc-212x300.jpg%20212w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668073%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EList%20of%20people%20who%20were%20served%20eviction%20notices%20in%20Tamulpur%20district%2C%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOsman%20Ali%20from%20the%20village%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20the%20village%20for%20over%20100%20years%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20put%20a%20notice%20in%20our%20local%20market%20to%20vacate%20our%20land.%20Though%20our%20land%20is%20in%20a%20tribal%20belt%20and%20block%20area%2C%20there%20are%20other%20communities%20too%20in%20this%20protected%20belt%20and%20block%2C%20including%20Bengali%20Hindus%20and%20Rajbanshis%3B%20however%2C%20only%20we%20got%20the%20notice%20of%20eviction%20in%20a%20selective%20manner.%20We%20have%20been%20living%20in%20this%20land%20since%20a%20time%20when%20there%20was%20no%20concept%20of%20tribal%20belts%20and%20blocks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-Muslim%20bias%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brutal%20tactic%20of%20evictions%20has%20increased%20in%20frequency%20against%20families%20such%20as%20Jesmina%E2%80%99s%2C%20causing%20irreparable%20damage%20to%20their%20livelihoods%20and%20psyche.%20In%202021%2C%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fassam-muslim-peasants-cultivating-land-decades-evicted-darrang-dis-3-reportedly-killed-firing%5C%22%3Eopened%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20unarmed%20landless%20peasants%20before%20bulldozing%20at%20least%205%2C000%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20in%20the%20Darrang%20District.%20Moinul%20Haque%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20cold%20blood%2C%20his%20body%20barbarically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F9%2F24%2Findia-assam-photographer-video-stomps-muslim-police%5C%22%3Estomped%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20depicted%20in%20a%20gruesome%20video%20that%20will%20remain%20a%20blot%20in%20the%20memories%20of%20the%20marginalised%20Miya%20people%20forever.%20Destroying%20children%E2%80%99s%20educational%20rights%20and%20futures%20is%20fine%20by%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20who%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-bjp-muslim-miya-3387725.html%5C%22%3Edoesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20Miya%20Muslims%20vote%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Othering%20and%20oppressing%20the%20Miyas%20successfully%20garnered%20the%20support%20of%20a%20sizable%20section%20of%20the%20majority.%20It%20is%20an%20evil%20tactic%2C%20with%20national%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-police-firing-darrang-eviction-drive-government%5C%22%3EAssam%20Firing%3A%20What%20Happened%20During%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Eviction%20Drive%20in%20Darrang%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20unabated%20destruction%20of%20homes%20is%20the%20newest%20development%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-quotes-amrit-kaal-14-times-in-august-15-speech-3264575%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20new%20slogan%20to%20describe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Famrit-kaal-meaning-origin-explained-union-budget-2022%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20vision%20of%20%E2%80%98100%25%20development%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99.%20The%20government%20is%20celebrating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Azadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20country%20is%20going%20to%20celebrate%20another%20Independence%20Day%2C%20thousands%20of%20%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20Muslims%20have%20been%20left%20in%20a%20state%20of%20limbo%20%E2%80%93%20without%20a%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20a%20home%2C%20and%20a%20future.%20Some%20more%20have%20received%20eviction%20notices%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Assam.%20These%20targeted%20evictions%20are%20not%20only%20against%20humanity%20but%20also%20against%20Article%2023-24%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20fundamental%20rights%20against%20exploitation.%20The%20preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20guarantees%20equality%20and%20individual%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98threat%E2%80%99%20they%20pose%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20encroachment%E2%80%9D%20on%20land%20or%20public%20resources.%20If%20the%20government%20can%20allot%20lands%20to%20controversial%20Indian%20yoga%20guru%20turned%20businessman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Findia-modi-ramdev%2F%5C%22%3EBaba%20Ramdev%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20owners%20of%20private%20enterprises%2C%20including%20tea%20gardens%2C%20why%20can%20it%20not%20give%20land%20to%20the%20poor%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20just%20to%20survive%3F%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2022%2FReport-No.-4-of-2022_English-063aa92eb7e3732.33325568.pdf%5C%22%3EAuditor%20General%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%2C%20are%20993%20police%20officers%20illegally%20living%20in%20government%20housing%20%E2%80%93%20probably%20the%20very%20same%20officers%20who%20are%20evicting%20families%20such%20as%20Jesmina%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%2C%20like%20%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20are%20squashed%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%20The%20%3Cem%3Egodi-%3C%2Fem%3Emedia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1040558%2Fwhy-eviction-drives-in-assam-are-no-longer-facing-resistance%5C%22%3Efalsely%20terms%3C%2Fa%3E%20innocent%20families%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20violent%20campaign%20to%20remove%20citizenship%20rights%20in%20the%20violent%20project%20of%20building%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20When%20the%20international%20media%20revealed%20this%20agenda%20in%20a%20recent%20BBC%20documentary%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20video%20was%20banned%2C%20and%20those%20who%20attended%20screenings%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-india-64407921%5C%22%3Edetained.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20families%20who%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20this%20violent%20agenda%20are%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20unheard%2C%20with%20no%20medium%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20of%20extreme%20sorrow%20to%20the%20international%20community%2C%20let%20alone%20their%20fellow%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20post-colonial%20Assam%2C%20Muslims%2C%20especially%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%2C%20have%20always%20been%20on%20the%20margin%20and%20under%20systematic%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-nrc-a-history-of-violence-and-persecution%5C%22%3Epersecution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Especially%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20power%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20using%20various%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Doubtful-voter%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20to%20harass%20the%20Miya%20community.%20Recently%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20has%20started%20utilising%20the%20eviction%20tool%20to%20make%20the%20people%20homeless%2C%20landless%2C%20jobless%2C%20and%20to%20strip%20them%20of%20their%20citizenship%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20government%20came%20out%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20arrest%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20youth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F03%2F10%2Findia-assam-child-underage-marriage%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20arrested%20from%20the%20marginalised%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Such%20exclusionary%20mechanism%20of%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20finds%20resonance%20in%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJP%20governments%20of%20various%20other%20states%2C%20including%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(currently%20under%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule).%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20central%20government%20is%20known%20for%20its%20anti-Muslim%20policies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20down-gradation%20of%20the%20statehood%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20landless%20people%20is%20growing%20thanks%20to%20annual%20floods%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsoil-erosion-has-left-nearly-90000-landless-in-assam-in-last-five-years-centre%5C%22%3Eerosion%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3Eriver%20banks.%20One%20is%20yet%20to%20understand%20what%20message%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-vishwaguru-india-world-hindutva%5C%22%3EVishwaguru%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20send%20by%20aggravating%20the%20threat%20of%20landlessness%20with%20the%20vast%20state%20machinery%20and%20its%20mighty%20force.%20This%20dark%20chapter%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20is%20unfolding%20in%20a%20state%20where%20new%20murals%20and%20paintings%20came%20up%20to%20host%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosters%20lined%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20slogans%20%E2%80%98the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%2C%E2%80%99%20are%20nothing%20to%20be%20proud%20of.%20It%20is%20high%20time%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20to%20note%20that%20targeted%20communal%20actions%20will%20irreversibly%20damage%20the%20pro