3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Rs%203.2%20crore%20jobs%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20those%20were%20worth%20Rs%203.2%20crore%2C%20even%20that%20may%20be%20okay.%20But%20Rs%203.2%20crore%20per%20moderately%20skilled%20job%20is%20too%20much.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20finally%2C%20above%20and%20beyond%20his%20criticisms%20of%20your%20analysis%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20also%20attacked%20you%20in%20personal%20terms.%20He%E2%80%99s%20accused%20you%20of%20lacking%20pride%2C%20self-respect%2C%20and%20even%20dignity%2C%20of%20bankruptcy%20of%20morals%2C%20and%20believe%20it%20or%20not%20of%20an%20over-simplistic%20mind.%20Do%20you%20really%20want%20to%20respond%20to%20that%20or%20do%20you%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20off%20just%20ignored%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20he%20used%20to%20be%20very%20polite%20when%20he%20came%20to%20the%20RBI%20and%20met%20me%20on%20some%20issue%20or%20the%20other.%20Let%20me%20not%20get%20into%20the%20language%20of%20the%20street%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20dignified.%20But%20I%20mean%20when%20people%20couch%20it%20with%20that%2C%20it%20makes%20debate%20much%20harder.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20both%20on%20the%20same%20side%20%E2%80%93%20we%20want%20jobs%20for%20India.%20What%20we%E2%80%99re%20disputing%20is%20whether%20the%20jobs%20will%20come%20through%20the%20scheme%20the%20government%20is%20suggesting.%20I%20really%20hope%20it%20will%2C%20but%20I%20would%20want%20the%20government%20to%20continuously%20evaluate%2C%20in%20an%20independent%20way%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20doing%20that%20and%20given%20that%20the%20data%20are%20so%20hard%20to%20get%2C%20and%20given%20even%20then%20it%20can%20be%20massaged%20and%20manipulated%2C%20you%20really%20need%20an%20independent%20evaluation%20agency%20to%20look%20at%20this%20to%20get%20the%20data%20to%20us.%20And%20why%20I%20say%20this%20is%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20expanding%20the%20scheme%20left%20right%20and%20centre%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20ask%20is%20this%20really%20the%20way%20to%20go%2C%20is%20the%20government%20actually%20better%20off%3F%20Because%20the%20country%20needs%20jobs%2C%20there%20are%20no%20two%20questions%20about%20it.%20How%20we%20produce%20those%20jobs%2C%20that%20to%20my%20mind%20is%20a%20central%20question%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20hear%20that%20addressed%20so%20far.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20me%20put%20you%20what%20someone%20said%20about%20the%20personal%20attack%20on%20you%20made%20by%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar.%20This%20person%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20only%20resort%20to%20vituperative%20language%20when%20actually%20they%20realise%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20got%20a%20good%20case%20to%20make.%20They%20buttress%20the%20bankruptcy%20of%20their%20arguments%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20using%20his%20language%20against%20him%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cby%20using%20the%20vituperative%20personal%20language%20instead.%E2%80%9D%20So%20does%20his%20personal%20critique%20of%20you%20suggest%20that%20actually%2C%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20got%20good%20arguments%20to%20make%20which%20is%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20speaking%20in%20these%20terms%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20would%20say%20after%20a%20six-page%20note%20%E2%80%93%20which%20again%20I%20think%20is%20commendable%20that%20he%20took%20the%20time%20to%20write%20it%20%E2%80%93%20he%20basically%20agrees%20with%20the%20argument%3A%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20assembly.%20And%20where%20he%20says%20%E2%80%98lies%2C%20lies%2C%20lies%2C%E2%80%99%20we%20said%2040%25%20to%2080%25%2C%20he%20says%2065%25.%20Well%20if%20that%E2%80%99s%20lies%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20live%20with%20those%20lies%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20part%20of%20the%20academic%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20he%20agrees%20with%20everything%20we%20say.%20The%20difference%20is%20he%20thinks%20good%20stuff%20is%20going%20to%20come%20in%20the%20future.%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20let%E2%80%99s%20be%20quite%20skeptical%20about%20that%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come.%20And%20if%20as%20he%20says%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20at%20this%20since%202014%2C%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20for%20nine%20years.%20You%20remember%20%5BAlbert%5D%20Einstein%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20insanity%3A%20doing%20the%20same%20thing%20and%20expecting%20a%20different%20result.%20%5B%3Cstrong%3EEditor%E2%80%99s%20note%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20quote%20is%20often%20attributed%20to%20Einstein%2C%20but%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fnews%2Fhere-are-6-things-albert-einstein-never-said%5C%22%3Eno%20evidence%20he%20said%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20I%20would%20hope%20this%20works%20because%20we%20are%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20in%20this%20scheme.%20But%20evaluate%20it.%20Put%20it%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20Tell%20the%20people%20of%20India%20this%20scheme%20is%20working%2C%20not%20through%20headlines%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20exporting.%20What%20are%20we%20creating%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs%3F%20How%20much%20are%20we%20getting%20for%20that%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20willing%20to%20believe%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20are%20getting%20employed.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20huge%20vulnerability%20in%20India%2C%20female%20labour%20force%20participation%20is%20very%20low.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20good%20thing.%20So%20come%20out%20with%20all%20these%20numbers.%20Show%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20incremental%2C%20not%20that%20this%20is%20stuff%20they%20were%20doing%20anyway%20but%20they%20did%20it%20because%20of%20the%20scheme.%20And%20tell%20us%2C%20how%20much%20does%20the%20scheme%20cost%20per%20job%20that%20we%20are%20creating.%20And%20will%20they%20stay%20once%20we%20stop%20paying%3F%20Now%2C%20already%20those%20manufacturers%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%2C%20you%20need%20to%20extend%20the%20scheme%20because%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20enough%20time.%E2%80%9D%