%20to%20this%20list%20cameras%2C%20printers%2C%20hard%20disks%2C%20telephonic%20devices.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20a%20whole%20range%20of%20things%20are%20certainly%20going%20to%20be%20put%20on%20restrictive%20import.%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20suggested%20that%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20ensure%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Ctrusted%20and%20verifiable%20systems%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20sounds%20as%20if%20he%E2%80%99s%20hinting%20at%20issues%20to%20do%20with%20national%20security.%20How%20do%20you%20view%20this%20decision%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20is%20an%20engineer.%20He%20should%20know%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20necessarily%20just%20the%20hardware%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20software%20that%E2%80%99s%20layered%20on%20top%20which%20is%20where%20the%20security%20issues%20are.%20I%20mean%20the%20government%2C%20you%20know%2C%20got%20into%20a%20row%20about%20Pegasus.%20That%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20the%20hardware%20that%20was%20about%20the%20software%20which%20allows%20for%20spying.%20And%20so%20security%20issues%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20the%20hardware%2C%20and%20if%20you%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20a%20particular%20country%E2%80%99s%20hardware%2C%20by%20all%20means%2C%20ban%20that.%20But%20you%20know%20given%20global%20supply%20chain%E2%80%99s%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20ban%20all%20imports.%20I%20mean%20the%20reality%20is%20we%20have%20been%20assembling%20some%20of%20the%20stuff%2C%20as%20I%20said%2C%20personal%20computers%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20moved%20forward%20beyond%20that.%20If%20this%20is%20about%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%20how%20do%20you%20think%20this%20is%20going%20to%20expand%3F%20And%20this%20again%20neglects%20the%20fact%20that%20at%20this%20point%20we%20should%20not%20be%20considering%20the%20lowest%20part%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20chain%20assembly.%20We%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20going%20to%20affect%20our%20services%20exports%20hugely.%20You%20know%2C%20AI%20is%20based%20on%20using%20the%20top%20quality%20computers%20which%20now%20China%20cannot%20get%20access%20to%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20denied%20some%20of%20those%20chips.%20We%20can%20still%20get%20access%20to%2C%20let%20us%20steal%20a%20march%20over%20them%2C%20but%20focus%20on%20the%20big%20picture%2C%20focus%20on%20the%20big%20things%2C%20not%20the%20tiny%20little%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStop%20putting%20the%20old%20license%20permit%20raj%20back%20into%20action.%20You%20know%2C%20this%20is%20really%20a%20failure%20of%20economic%20thinking.%20And%20this%20I%20think%20is%20the%20bigger%20problem%20from%20these%20kinds%20of%20schemes.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20succeeded%2C%20you%20think%20you%20have%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20extend%20it%20everywhere%20else%2C%20and%20then%20you%20realize%20you%E2%80%99ve%20brought%20back%20the%20license%20permit%20raj.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20use%20the%20term%20licensing.%20I%20was%20shocked%20that%20they%20would%20use%20the%20term%20licensing%2C%20given%20what%20a%20bad%20reputation%20it%20has%20in%20India.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20is%20the%20way%20to%20go%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20missing%20out%20on%20our%20biggest%20advantage%20which%20is%20our%20high-quality%20services.%20If%20you%20put%20taxes%2C%20restrictions%20on%20computers%20and%20iPads%20etc.%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20restricting%20that%20industry%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20forcing%20them%20to%20go%20begging%20to%20the%20government%20every%20few%20months%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20need%20more%20of%20this%2C%20I%20need%20more%20of%20that.%E2%80%9D%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20logic%20behind%20this%2C%20let%20me%20leave%20it%20at%20that.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20said%20something%20very%20evocative%20which%20I%20will%20repeat%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20failure%20of%20economic%20thinking%E2%80%9D.%20And%20I%20take%20it%20that%E2%80%99s%20as%20true%20as%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20put%20a%20range%20of%20restrictions%20on%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20imports%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20just%20mentioned%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20true%20of%20the%20PLI%20scheme.%20You%20haven%E2%80%99t%20thought%20this%20through%3B%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20asked%20yourself%20the%20question%20does%20it%20work%3B%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20asked%20yourself%20the%20question%20could%20the%20money%20be%20spent%20better%20on%20other%20things%3B%20and%20finally%2C%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20asked%20the%20question%20should%20India%20be%20getting%20into%20different%20areas%20rather%20than%20manufacturing%3F%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%20that%20rigorous%20thinking%20that%20you%20expect%20ministers%20to%20do%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20duty%20and%20responsibility%2C%20they%20are%20clearly%20not%20doing%20%E2%80%93%20or%20at%20least%20not%20adequately.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I%20will%20leave%20that%20summary%20from%20you%20as%20the%20final%20word%2C%20other%20than%20saying.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20a%20bigger%20debate%20about%20the%20direction%20we%E2%80%99re%20going%20because%20I%20am%20very%20worried.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20direction%2C%20given%20the%20many%20pressures%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%20the%20onshoring%2C%20nearshoring%20that%20is%20happening%2C%20the%20automation%20that%E2%80%99s%20happening%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20China%2C%20Vietnam%20are%20desperately%20competing%20for%20these%20kinds%20of%20businesses%2C%20do%20we%20have%20a%20vision%20on%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20going%20forward%3F%20And%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20it%20in%20the%20government%20utterances.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20I%20can%20say%20is%20I%20hope%20Mr%20Chandrase