al%20rights%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vedhapriya%20has%20specialised%20in%20wildlife%20rescue%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613-264x300.jpg%20264w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613-500x568.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613-768x873.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fvedha4-1691583613-150x171.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVedhapriya%20has%20specialised%20in%20wildlife%20rescue.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20only%20a%20few%20women%20in%20this%20field%20today%2C%20and%20Vedhapriya%20says%20that%20occasionally%2C%20she%20faces%20uncomfortable%20situations%20while%20executing%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20qualities%20that%20is%20needed%20while%20rescuing%20a%20snake%20is%20crowd%20management.%20We%20must%20not%20lose%20our%20cool%20or%20focus.%20The%20snake%20is%20already%20under%20stress%3B%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20stressed%20too.%20But%20in%20certain%20areas%2C%20people%20are%20very%20uncouth.%20They%20speak%20in%20a%20way%20that%20makes%20you%20feel%20uncomfortable.%20I%20still%20manage%20to%20maintain%20my%20composure%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20task%20at%20hand%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20for%20this%20composure%20and%20skill%20that%20she%